1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:29,980
[SPEAKER_01] "Povo, da, kako, da, kako, svoj." "Nijedan dan nisam bio nesvrta." "Bona seda." "Fanje, nisu si Marija, dragi gledatelji portala Mreže Riječi." "Gledate drugu epizodu podcasta Male škole teologije u kojem razgovaramo o raznim teološkim temama. Prva tema je bila kršćanska duhovnost, a sada prelazimo na korizmu. S nama još uvijek Don Mladen, doma.

2
00:00:29,980 --> 00:00:59,960
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala da ne pozdravljamo vas opet." "Hvala nisu si Marija, lijep pozdrav vama i svim gledateljima ovog podkasta." "Evo da se nadovežemo na prvu epizodu, sada govorimo o korizmi. Zašto je ona važna u kršćanskoj duhovnosti?" "Crkvena godina je podijeljena na liturgijska vremena. Imamo, kako to kaže liturgija crkve, dosad sama kako crkva uči, postoje snažna i, recimo tako, obična liturgijska vremena. U toj podijeli crkvene godine korizma

3
00:00:59,960 --> 00:01:21,959
[SPEAKER_00] se ubraja u snažna liturgijska vremena. Dakle, kad se kaže snažna ili jaka liturgijska vremena, želi se reći da crkva kroz to vrijeme svoje djeci sugerira neke sadržaje kako bi na malo jedan ozbiljniji način proživjeli to vrijeme, a sve sa nakanom da se dolično pripravi za proslavu Uskrsa.

4
00:01:21,959 --> 00:01:27,959
[SPEAKER_00] jer je Uskrst ubiti temeljni blagdan u kršanskoj vjeri, pa o tome onda korizma i služi."

5
00:01:27,959 --> 00:01:34,959
[SPEAKER_01] Bili ste sada spomenuli da je Uskrst temeljni blagdan. Neki bi čak rekli zašto ne Božić ako je riječ o utjelovljenju?

6
00:01:34,959 --> 00:01:47,959
[SPEAKER_00] Božić je, odnosno Kristovo utjelovljenje, ako ćemo baš tako ne podloga svega, jer je Kristovo utjelovljenje, rođenje, u biti Pavao u Efežanima i drugim svojim posljednicima govori o Kristovo otajstvu.

7
00:01:47,959 --> 00:02:00,959
[SPEAKER_00] Sva otajstva od njegova utjelovljenja do njegova uzašašća u nebesku slavu čine otajstvo Isusa Hrista. I kako kažemo u vjeravanju, sva su radi nas i našeg spasenja.

8
00:02:00,959 --> 00:02:16,159
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ako pristupimo pojedinačno tim otajstvima u otajstvo Isusa Hrista, tada nema sumnje da je uskresnuće nekako, i Pavao o tome, prvo je Korinčan 15. poglavlje, Pavao o tome prepoznaje temelj naše vjere.

9
00:02:16,159 --> 00:02:24,340
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, Kristus uskresnuće je kamen zaglavni kršćanstva. Kaže Pavao, ako Krist nije uskresnuo, zaluduje naše vjere. Čemu se nadamo?

10
00:02:24,580 --> 00:02:34,539
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, njegovu uskresnuće, pobjeda na smrću, je poruka da će ta pobjeda na smrću u njegovom životu, na neki način, biti i za nas. Ona je pobjeda i za nas.

11
00:02:34,539 --> 00:02:43,919
[SPEAKER_00] A u biti, svi, kako bih rekao ja, moj kolega, svi naši strahovi, sva religija, potječe iz pitanja straha o smrti.

12
00:02:43,919 --> 00:02:52,240
[SPEAKER_00] A krišanstvo ima odgovor na taj strah o smrti, što? Poslije života. Krišanstvo ima odgovor, poslije života nastavlja se život, ali život vječni.

13
00:02:52,379 --> 00:03:02,759
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ono za što mi žudimo, to gospodin Bog nudi o tajstvu Krista uskresnuća i nudi nama, otvara nam vrata, također, život vječni po Kristu.

14
00:03:02,759 --> 00:03:09,500
[SPEAKER_01] Dotaknimo se, dakle, i te pobožnosti križnog puta, sada kada već govorimo o uskresnuću.

15
00:03:09,500 --> 00:03:17,939
[SPEAKER_01] Naime, može li nam to razmatranje Kristove muke pomoći da se i mi približimo, dakle, tomu tajstvu?

16
00:03:18,240 --> 00:03:29,080
[SPEAKER_00] Pa naravno, ovako, kad nas crkva poziva da nemam plodona sa način, proživimo vrijeme korizme, a ono, običajno, kažem, ima 40 dana.

17
00:03:29,080 --> 00:03:31,860
[SPEAKER_00] Možda bi jednu rečenicu treba reći kako su došlo do broja 40.

18
00:03:32,699 --> 00:03:40,159
[SPEAKER_00] Naime, došlo se, prvo korizma se razvija negdje od četvog stoljeća, prije je bila neka kraća priprava za proslavu uskresanu.

19
00:03:40,159 --> 00:03:51,900
[SPEAKER_00] Kad je uskres ustaljen na prvu nedjelju za mladom mjesecu proljeće, tada je praktički nekako se razvio običaj da se ta priprava za proslav uskresa provode kroz 40 dana.

20
00:03:53,560 --> 00:04:08,340
[SPEAKER_00] Nije uvijek bilo počinjeno sa pepelnicom, nego malo drugačije, svakako po uzoru na Krista, koji na početku svog javnog poslanja provio 40 dana u pustinji, pa i po uzoru na 40 godina hoda kroz pustinju židovskog naroda,

21
00:04:08,340 --> 00:04:23,379
[SPEAKER_00] razvijao se korizmeno vrijeme od 40 dana. Makar ako točno mjerimo, nećemo baš lako doći do broja 40, jer od pepeljnice do uskresa ima praktički 46 dana,

22
00:04:23,379 --> 00:04:34,519
[SPEAKER_00] ali ako maknemo praktički šest nedjelja korizmenih, doći ćemo onda negdje do 40 dana,

23
00:04:34,519 --> 00:04:46,339
[SPEAKER_00] s tim da onda tu treba uračunati i vazmenu subotu, i veliki petak i veliku subotu, s tim da vazmenu trudnevlje, makar nije posebno liturgijsko vrijeme,

24
00:04:46,339 --> 00:04:55,980
[SPEAKER_00] ipak čini jedan zaseban dio liturgijsko godine, veliki tjedan, ali osobno vazmenu trudnevlje, dakle veliki četvrtak, veliki petak i vazmenu bijenje.

25
00:04:57,079 --> 00:05:11,660
[SPEAKER_00] Svakako, na početku korizme, na slijedu pepeljnice, crkva stavlja pred nas tri sredstva, to je iz jedan dio gospodina govora na gori, stavlja molitvu, stavlja post i stavlja dijela milosrđa.

26
00:05:11,660 --> 00:05:22,079
[SPEAKER_00] U drugim riječima, kroz ta tri sredstva želi se na neki način potaknuti vjernike, da porade na svom odnosu prema gospodinom Bogu, prema bližnjima i prema sebi samima.

27
00:05:22,079 --> 00:05:35,779
[SPEAKER_00] U tom korizmenom hodu, svakako, kad je riječ o molitvi, privilegerano mjesto pripada pobožnosti križnog puta, u kojem kršarski život nije drugo doli hod za istom kristom, ili trebao bi hod za istom kristom.

28
00:05:35,779 --> 00:05:50,079
[SPEAKER_00] Razmatrajući postaje njegova križnog puta, koje su u biti izraz njegove ljubavi prema nama, onda se i mi motiviramo na jedan dublji, jedan bolji, jedan plodonosniji način živjeti ljuba prema dragom Bogu i braća i sestrama.

29
00:05:50,459 --> 00:05:58,279
[SPEAKER_01] Sada ste bili spomenuli, dakle, nešto što nas još čeka u ovom periodu je post i nemrs. Biste li nam mogli objasni koja je razlika?

30
00:05:58,279 --> 00:06:16,100
[SPEAKER_00] Pa, post je jedna važna dimenzija križnog svog života. Mi smo to danas, a i crkva je tako svojim odredama odredila, postali smo jako nemarni prema postu.

31
00:06:16,100 --> 00:06:21,959
[SPEAKER_00] A post može imati jednu silnu snagu za naš križnjan život i treba imati.

32
00:06:21,959 --> 00:06:35,920
[SPEAKER_00] Kad se kaže post, crkva propisuje u priliku ovako, post je uzeti hrane dostatno do sitosti jedan put dnevno i jedan put ili dva put malo.

33
00:06:35,920 --> 00:06:46,759
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, jedan put se najs do sitosti, a dva put do malo. A ubiti to je ono što praktički masa vjernika danas živi. Osobno to starijih ljudi.

34
00:06:47,920 --> 00:06:59,759
[SPEAKER_00] U našem narodu se je razvijelo, ja znam to iz moje obiteljske kuće, kad bi Matija rekla da posti, to je bilo kruh i voda. To je post. O kruhu i vodi ili samo o vodi cijeli dan.

35
00:06:59,759 --> 00:07:08,920
[SPEAKER_00] Ali kako su teško radili, onda je bilo o kruhu i vodi, uglavnom se petak posti, o kruhu i voda. I to je ono što ja smatam da je post.

36
00:07:09,680 --> 00:07:17,720
[SPEAKER_00] Nemars kaže da se treba ustegnuti od mesa i mesnih prarađevina tog dana i poste Nemars Trkva zapovide samo na dva dana.

37
00:07:17,720 --> 00:07:23,019
[SPEAKER_00] Na čistu srijedu, dakle na pepelicu i na veliki petak.

38
00:07:23,019 --> 00:07:31,439
[SPEAKER_00] Ja bih rekao da, odnosno ako smijem, ja bih potao ko vjernike da puno ozbiljnije prestupaju stvarnosti posta

39
00:07:31,439 --> 00:07:37,540
[SPEAKER_00] i da ako mogu, zbog zdravstvenih razloga, da poste u kruhu i vodi svaki petak.

40
00:07:37,540 --> 00:07:43,420
[SPEAKER_00] Osobito korizmene petke, jer post u sebi ima silnu duhovnu snagu.

41
00:07:43,420 --> 00:07:56,300
[SPEAKER_00] Prvo, post poručuje, mi kad uzimamo hranu, naše tijelo iz hrane uzima one sastavke, minerale, proteine, bilančene

42
00:07:56,300 --> 00:07:58,100
[SPEAKER_00] koje su potrebne za održanje biloškog života.

43
00:07:58,100 --> 00:08:01,660
[SPEAKER_00] I možemo zaključiti, hrana mi je potrebna za život.

44
00:08:01,660 --> 00:08:08,899
[SPEAKER_00] A kada ja kažem, odreću se hrane, ja time implicito priznajem da je izvor moj života negdje drugdje.

45
00:08:08,899 --> 00:08:10,480
[SPEAKER_00] On je gospodinu Bogu.

46
00:08:10,480 --> 00:08:12,339
[SPEAKER_00] Bog je izvor moj života.

47
00:08:12,339 --> 00:08:16,319
[SPEAKER_00] I hranu mi će, Bog je izvor moj života.

48
00:08:17,040 --> 00:08:24,980
[SPEAKER_00] Drugo, potreba postaje jako važna, ne samo zbog ove, rekao bih, dogmatsko-teološke dimenzije,

49
00:08:24,980 --> 00:08:30,680
[SPEAKER_00] ove vertikale, naše odnose prema gospodinu Bogu, nego zbog druge, ne manje važne dimenzije,

50
00:08:30,680 --> 00:08:32,399
[SPEAKER_00] a to je sam naš duhovni život.

51
00:08:33,240 --> 00:08:42,259
[SPEAKER_00] Mi smo u svome čovještvu jedinstvo naših vegetativnih, emocionalnih, psiholoških, psihičkih i duhovnih snaga.

52
00:08:42,259 --> 00:08:44,159
[SPEAKER_00] Sve se tu u nama isprepleće.

53
00:08:44,159 --> 00:08:46,659
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, sve dimenzije razli u nama se isprepleću.

54
00:08:46,659 --> 00:08:51,620
[SPEAKER_00] I zbog ranjenosti istočnim grijehom, ono što nazivamo tijelo,

55
00:08:51,620 --> 00:08:56,820
[SPEAKER_00] a to su moja nagnuća, moje sklonosti, moje požudne moći.

56
00:08:56,820 --> 00:09:00,440
[SPEAKER_00] One su toliko jake da izmiču u kontroli mog razuma.

57
00:09:00,440 --> 00:09:01,840
[SPEAKER_00] Ne mogu njima vlada.

58
00:09:01,840 --> 00:09:04,120
[SPEAKER_00] Pa to je iskustvo našeg pada u grijeh.

59
00:09:04,120 --> 00:09:05,159
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto padamo u grijeh?

60
00:09:05,159 --> 00:09:05,940
[SPEAKER_00] Nešto bi smo htjeli.

61
00:09:05,940 --> 00:09:07,620
[SPEAKER_00] Padamo iz svoje slabosti.

62
00:09:07,620 --> 00:09:10,840
[SPEAKER_00] Padamo iz svoje ljuskosti.

63
00:09:10,840 --> 00:09:12,139
[SPEAKER_00] Iz svog ograničenja.

64
00:09:12,139 --> 00:09:18,620
[SPEAKER_00] Post, kad postim, ja postom te snage koje izmiču u kontroli mog uma, mog razuma,

65
00:09:18,620 --> 00:09:20,039
[SPEAKER_00] čak i razuma koju osjetljam vjerom,

66
00:09:20,379 --> 00:09:22,100
[SPEAKER_00] ja ih stavljam pod kontrolu.

67
00:09:22,100 --> 00:09:23,460
[SPEAKER_00] Kad kajem sebi neću.

68
00:09:23,460 --> 00:09:26,519
[SPEAKER_00] Neću uzeti komad hrane.

69
00:09:26,519 --> 00:09:27,919
[SPEAKER_00] Neću ogovarati.

70
00:09:27,919 --> 00:09:30,080
[SPEAKER_00] Neću gledati primjerine sadržaje.

71
00:09:30,080 --> 00:09:31,500
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, neću.

72
00:09:31,500 --> 00:09:37,940
[SPEAKER_00] Ja tada praktički, evo, pomažem ovoj ovladavanju svog života.

73
00:09:37,940 --> 00:09:41,740
[SPEAKER_00] A to je silno važno u korizmenom vremenu.

74
00:09:41,740 --> 00:09:43,480
[SPEAKER_00] Znat ovlada svojim životom.

75
00:09:43,480 --> 00:09:46,120
[SPEAKER_00] Znat ovladati onim što se u meni događa,

76
00:09:46,120 --> 00:09:48,120
[SPEAKER_00] onim nagnućima, protegnućima,

77
00:09:48,120 --> 00:09:50,299
[SPEAKER_00] koji često puta završavaju ukušnju,

78
00:09:50,379 --> 00:09:53,100
[SPEAKER_00] a preko kušnje završavaju u grijeh.

79
00:09:53,100 --> 00:09:54,879
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, to me posluži.

80
00:09:54,879 --> 00:09:57,519
[SPEAKER_00] Ako bismo još jednu riječ reći,

81
00:09:57,519 --> 00:09:59,779
[SPEAKER_00] danas nam je, mislim, danas je danas,

82
00:09:59,779 --> 00:10:01,159
[SPEAKER_00] dvije stvari su nam važne,

83
00:10:01,159 --> 00:10:02,320
[SPEAKER_00] kao kruh nasušni.

84
00:10:02,320 --> 00:10:05,200
[SPEAKER_00] Kao, kao, rekao bih, kao kruh.

85
00:10:05,659 --> 00:10:07,120
[SPEAKER_00] Prva jaskeza očiju.

86
00:10:07,120 --> 00:10:10,279
[SPEAKER_00] Da znam kontroloirati što gledam.

87
00:10:10,279 --> 00:10:12,980
[SPEAKER_00] Negdje medicina kaže, čini mi se da sam negdje pročitao,

88
00:10:12,980 --> 00:10:16,559
[SPEAKER_00] da negdje preko 95% svih spoznaja koje čovjek stječe,

89
00:10:16,559 --> 00:10:17,980
[SPEAKER_00] dolazi preko očiju.

90
00:10:17,980 --> 00:10:20,179
[SPEAKER_00] U svjetlu vida je silno važno.

91
00:10:20,179 --> 00:10:22,620
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, i mi po vidu,

92
00:10:22,620 --> 00:10:24,200
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, izvanski svijet,

93
00:10:24,860 --> 00:10:27,100
[SPEAKER_00] promatramo ga i po vidu,

94
00:10:27,100 --> 00:10:28,879
[SPEAKER_00] kroz slike koje dolaze u naš um,

95
00:10:28,879 --> 00:10:31,279
[SPEAKER_00] mi dolazimo do spoznaje o svijetu,

96
00:10:31,279 --> 00:10:33,700
[SPEAKER_00] ali i u sebi koji živimo u tom svijetu.

97
00:10:33,700 --> 00:10:37,100
[SPEAKER_00] To je, dakle,

98
00:10:37,100 --> 00:10:39,559
[SPEAKER_00] i ne kaže se bez veze

99
00:10:39,559 --> 00:10:41,179
[SPEAKER_00] da su oči, prozori duše.

100
00:10:41,179 --> 00:10:42,500
[SPEAKER_00] Kroz te prozore,

101
00:10:42,500 --> 00:10:43,759
[SPEAKER_00] kroz druga osjetila,

102
00:10:43,759 --> 00:10:44,860
[SPEAKER_00] sadržaj svijeta,

103
00:10:44,860 --> 00:10:46,100
[SPEAKER_00] olaze moj unutarnji svijet.

104
00:10:46,100 --> 00:10:49,220
[SPEAKER_00] Kako nam je danas potrebno malo činiti

105
00:10:49,220 --> 00:10:50,299
[SPEAKER_00] askezu očiju,

106
00:10:50,299 --> 00:10:52,259
[SPEAKER_00] da ne gledam što ne trebam gledati.

107
00:10:52,259 --> 00:10:54,200
[SPEAKER_00] Da biram sadržaj

108
00:10:54,200 --> 00:10:55,840
[SPEAKER_00] što slušati, što gledati.

109
00:10:55,840 --> 00:10:58,419
[SPEAKER_00] A još je važnija od ove askeze očiju,

110
00:10:58,419 --> 00:11:00,399
[SPEAKER_00] važna je ono što smo zaboravili,

111
00:11:00,399 --> 00:11:01,779
[SPEAKER_00] a to je šutnja.

112
00:11:01,779 --> 00:11:04,899
[SPEAKER_00] Ne govoriti kad ne treba.

113
00:11:04,899 --> 00:11:06,399
[SPEAKER_00] Znati šutjeti,

114
00:11:06,399 --> 00:11:08,279
[SPEAKER_00] znati primjereno govoriti,

115
00:11:08,279 --> 00:11:09,840
[SPEAKER_00] znati birati riječi,

116
00:11:09,840 --> 00:11:11,240
[SPEAKER_00] kako nam je to potrebno.

117
00:11:11,240 --> 00:11:13,679
[SPEAKER_00] U vremenu kad svatko želi govoriti,

118
00:11:13,679 --> 00:11:15,340
[SPEAKER_00] društvene mrežne im omogućavaju

119
00:11:15,340 --> 00:11:17,299
[SPEAKER_00] da bude subjekt nekakvih društvenih procesa,

120
00:11:17,299 --> 00:11:20,200
[SPEAKER_00] ih svak smatra da ima nešto za reći,

121
00:11:20,200 --> 00:11:21,460
[SPEAKER_00] pa bila to psovuka,

122
00:11:21,460 --> 00:11:22,419
[SPEAKER_00] bilo to vrijeđanje,

123
00:11:22,539 --> 00:11:24,720
[SPEAKER_00] svakako previše zagađenog

124
00:11:24,720 --> 00:11:26,860
[SPEAKER_00] od društvenih prostora

125
00:11:26,860 --> 00:11:27,960
[SPEAKER_00] u nama i oko nas,

126
00:11:27,960 --> 00:11:29,279
[SPEAKER_00] preko društvenih mreža,

127
00:11:29,279 --> 00:11:30,860
[SPEAKER_00] i zato nam je potrebna šutnja,

128
00:11:30,860 --> 00:11:33,740
[SPEAKER_00] da se riječ koja se treba

129
00:11:33,740 --> 00:11:35,379
[SPEAKER_00] izreći porodi u šutnji,

130
00:11:35,379 --> 00:11:35,940
[SPEAKER_00] u tišini,

131
00:11:35,940 --> 00:11:37,259
[SPEAKER_00] da bude smislena,

132
00:11:37,259 --> 00:11:38,519
[SPEAKER_00] da bude izgrađujuća,

133
00:11:38,519 --> 00:11:39,620
[SPEAKER_00] da bude dobra

134
00:11:39,620 --> 00:11:41,399
[SPEAKER_00] i korizma na to poziva,

135
00:11:41,399 --> 00:11:43,080
[SPEAKER_00] pazi na svoju riječ,

136
00:11:43,080 --> 00:11:44,419
[SPEAKER_00] pazi na govor,

137
00:11:44,419 --> 00:11:45,840
[SPEAKER_00] pazi na sebe.

138
00:11:47,440 --> 00:11:49,779
[SPEAKER_01] Zato da se nadovežem na ovo što ste malo prije rekli,

139
00:11:49,779 --> 00:11:50,960
[SPEAKER_01] naime,

140
00:11:50,960 --> 00:11:55,220
[SPEAKER_01] koja je svrha tog neću ili odrijećem se u ovom periodu,

141
00:11:55,220 --> 00:11:57,379
[SPEAKER_01] jer neko koje je sad van katoličkih krugova,

142
00:11:57,379 --> 00:11:58,019
[SPEAKER_01] rekao,

143
00:11:58,019 --> 00:11:59,179
[SPEAKER_01] pa zašto vaš bog,

144
00:11:59,179 --> 00:12:00,379
[SPEAKER_01] koji je naime dobar,

145
00:12:00,379 --> 00:12:01,279
[SPEAKER_01] milosrni bog,

146
00:12:01,279 --> 00:12:03,139
[SPEAKER_01] zašto on želi od vas da trpite,

147
00:12:03,139 --> 00:12:04,120
[SPEAKER_01] da se odrijećete?

148
00:12:04,120 --> 00:12:05,679
[SPEAKER_00] Koja je svrha?

149
00:12:05,759 --> 00:12:07,899
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, pa mislim da sve i djelamo odgovore na to pitanje,

150
00:12:07,899 --> 00:12:09,879
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, zbog ovladavanja sobom,

151
00:12:09,879 --> 00:12:12,940
[SPEAKER_00] Bog mi sa svoje strane nudi sve milosti,

152
00:12:12,940 --> 00:12:14,980
[SPEAKER_00] darove potrebne za život njegova djeteta,

153
00:12:14,980 --> 00:12:17,120
[SPEAKER_00] ali nudi konkretnom čovjeku,

154
00:12:17,120 --> 00:12:18,379
[SPEAKER_00] a taj konkretni čovjek,

155
00:12:18,379 --> 00:12:19,740
[SPEAKER_00] ja, vi, bilo tko,

156
00:12:19,740 --> 00:12:20,559
[SPEAKER_00] svaki vjerni,

157
00:12:20,559 --> 00:12:22,299
[SPEAKER_00] svi smo mi ranjeni.

158
00:12:22,299 --> 00:12:25,519
[SPEAKER_00] Teologija kaže da smo ranjeni ranom istošnog,

159
00:12:25,519 --> 00:12:26,919
[SPEAKER_00] ono što naziva ranom istošnog grijeha,

160
00:12:26,919 --> 00:12:28,820
[SPEAKER_00] on se, da kako u krštenju briše,

161
00:12:28,820 --> 00:12:30,779
[SPEAKER_00] kao i svi naši osobini grijece,

162
00:12:30,779 --> 00:12:32,059
[SPEAKER_00] ako smo kršteni odlasli dobi,

163
00:12:32,059 --> 00:12:33,799
[SPEAKER_00] ali ostaje posljedice tog grijeha,

164
00:12:33,799 --> 00:12:35,700
[SPEAKER_00] a posljedice su unutarnji nered.

165
00:12:35,700 --> 00:12:36,860
[SPEAKER_00] Jedna sklonost,

166
00:12:36,860 --> 00:12:39,740
[SPEAKER_00] to teologija naziva jednom latinskim izrazom,

167
00:12:39,740 --> 00:12:41,059
[SPEAKER_00] konkupiciencija,

168
00:12:41,059 --> 00:12:42,100
[SPEAKER_00] to znači požuda,

169
00:12:42,100 --> 00:12:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] ali ja bih rekao,

170
00:12:43,000 --> 00:12:43,879
[SPEAKER_00] to je jedna ranjenost,

171
00:12:43,879 --> 00:12:44,779
[SPEAKER_00] jedna slabost,

172
00:12:44,779 --> 00:12:46,279
[SPEAKER_00] po kojoj mi uvijek iznova,

173
00:12:46,279 --> 00:12:47,019
[SPEAKER_00] nekako,

174
00:12:47,019 --> 00:12:49,259
[SPEAKER_00] ako ne pazimo na sebe,

175
00:12:49,259 --> 00:12:51,700
[SPEAKER_00] završćemo u kušnju napad,

176
00:12:51,700 --> 00:12:52,600
[SPEAKER_00] završćemo u grijeh.

177
00:12:52,600 --> 00:12:53,980
[SPEAKER_00] A grijeh je,

178
00:12:53,980 --> 00:12:55,940
[SPEAKER_00] to je jedna kategorija, opet,

179
00:12:55,940 --> 00:12:57,779
[SPEAKER_00] u kojoj ne možemo ne govoriti,

180
00:12:57,779 --> 00:12:59,159
[SPEAKER_00] jer je, kaže,

181
00:12:59,440 --> 00:13:01,519
[SPEAKER_00] tamo Petar u prvoj posljedice,

182
00:13:01,519 --> 00:13:03,320
[SPEAKER_00] on grijeha naše ponese na drvu,

183
00:13:03,320 --> 00:13:05,779
[SPEAKER_00] da mi umriješi grijecima pravednosti živimo.

184
00:13:05,779 --> 00:13:07,679
[SPEAKER_00] Ako maknemo o grijeh iz svog života,

185
00:13:07,679 --> 00:13:10,700
[SPEAKER_00] mi ne znamo što je dijelo otkupljenja,

186
00:13:10,700 --> 00:13:12,159
[SPEAKER_00] što je Krist učinio za nas.

187
00:13:12,159 --> 00:13:14,220
[SPEAKER_00] Mi to ne razumimo onda.

188
00:13:14,220 --> 00:13:15,480
[SPEAKER_00] Možda to je malo poslije,

189
00:13:15,480 --> 00:13:18,440
[SPEAKER_00] ako budete u tom smjeru vodili razgovor.

190
00:13:18,440 --> 00:13:19,120
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

191
00:13:19,120 --> 00:13:20,539
[SPEAKER_00] i upravo ova askeza,

192
00:13:20,539 --> 00:13:22,059
[SPEAKER_00] ovo odricanje mi pomaže

193
00:13:22,059 --> 00:13:24,220
[SPEAKER_00] u toj borbi sa grijehom.

194
00:13:25,720 --> 00:13:26,639
[SPEAKER_00] Zarazumijete ovo,

195
00:13:26,639 --> 00:13:29,840
[SPEAKER_00] to će svako razumijeti,

196
00:13:29,840 --> 00:13:32,879
[SPEAKER_00] koji ima neke iskustva borbe,

197
00:13:32,879 --> 00:13:33,820
[SPEAKER_00] duhovne borbe,

198
00:13:33,820 --> 00:13:37,639
[SPEAKER_00] ko zaista radi na sebi,

199
00:13:37,639 --> 00:13:40,539
[SPEAKER_00] ko se trudi rasti u duhovnom životu,

200
00:13:40,539 --> 00:13:44,500
[SPEAKER_00] taj zna kako se teško oduprijeti zlo,

201
00:13:44,500 --> 00:13:46,940
[SPEAKER_00] kako je teško ne ogovarati,

202
00:13:46,940 --> 00:13:48,860
[SPEAKER_00] kako je teško ne uprijeti prstom,

203
00:13:49,179 --> 00:13:50,740
[SPEAKER_00] kako je teško ne usuditi,

204
00:13:50,740 --> 00:13:51,940
[SPEAKER_00] kako je teško,

205
00:13:51,940 --> 00:13:52,460
[SPEAKER_00] dakle,

206
00:13:52,460 --> 00:13:54,559
[SPEAKER_00] ostati čista srca,

207
00:13:54,559 --> 00:13:56,059
[SPEAKER_00] kako gospodin ona zahtjeva.

208
00:13:56,059 --> 00:13:57,960
[SPEAKER_00] I, dakle,

209
00:13:57,960 --> 00:13:59,879
[SPEAKER_00] dragi Bog sa svoje strane nudi sve

210
00:13:59,879 --> 00:14:00,600
[SPEAKER_00] i daje sve,

211
00:14:00,600 --> 00:14:02,019
[SPEAKER_00] ali traži moju soradnju.

212
00:14:02,019 --> 00:14:03,320
[SPEAKER_00] A ne mogu,

213
00:14:03,320 --> 00:14:04,820
[SPEAKER_00] ono što Bog nudi,

214
00:14:04,820 --> 00:14:06,120
[SPEAKER_00] ne mogu prihvatiti

215
00:14:06,120 --> 00:14:08,159
[SPEAKER_00] i to na neki način učini

216
00:14:08,159 --> 00:14:09,820
[SPEAKER_00] da to procvijete u mojom životu

217
00:14:09,820 --> 00:14:11,360
[SPEAKER_00] bez odricanja,

218
00:14:11,360 --> 00:14:13,139
[SPEAKER_00] bez rada na sebi,

219
00:14:13,139 --> 00:14:15,620
[SPEAKER_00] bez jednog napora

220
00:14:15,620 --> 00:14:17,960
[SPEAKER_00] da steknem određenu samokontrolu

221
00:14:17,960 --> 00:14:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] nad svojim životom.

222
00:14:20,000 --> 00:14:22,639
[SPEAKER_00] Makar i to treba opet

223
00:14:22,639 --> 00:14:26,659
[SPEAKER_00] shvatiti na ispravan način.

224
00:14:26,659 --> 00:14:27,700
[SPEAKER_00] Kad kažem samokontrolu,

225
00:14:27,700 --> 00:14:28,820
[SPEAKER_00] ispalo bi da su mi,

226
00:14:28,820 --> 00:14:30,620
[SPEAKER_00] glavni djelaci duhovnog života,

227
00:14:30,620 --> 00:14:31,379
[SPEAKER_00] i na neki način

228
00:14:31,379 --> 00:14:33,159
[SPEAKER_00] mi ćemo sebe dovesti u red.

229
00:14:33,159 --> 00:14:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nećemo.

230
00:14:34,000 --> 00:14:35,379
[SPEAKER_00] Nikada.

231
00:14:35,379 --> 00:14:37,460
[SPEAKER_00] Bez Božije pomoći nećemo.

232
00:14:37,460 --> 00:14:38,379
[SPEAKER_00] I to je,

233
00:14:38,379 --> 00:14:39,740
[SPEAKER_00] crkva je vrlo jasna,

234
00:14:39,740 --> 00:14:41,720
[SPEAKER_00] bez milosti ne možemo dobro učiniti

235
00:14:41,720 --> 00:14:42,700
[SPEAKER_00] niti dobro ustrajati.

236
00:14:42,700 --> 00:14:43,480
[SPEAKER_00] Drugim riječima,

237
00:14:43,480 --> 00:14:43,899
[SPEAKER_00] rekao bih,

238
00:14:43,899 --> 00:14:44,820
[SPEAKER_00] ovo od rica ima

239
00:14:44,820 --> 00:14:46,700
[SPEAKER_00] još jedan veći cilj,

240
00:14:46,700 --> 00:14:47,220
[SPEAKER_00] a to je

241
00:14:47,220 --> 00:14:48,879
[SPEAKER_00] prepustiti Boku kontrolu

242
00:14:48,879 --> 00:14:49,799
[SPEAKER_00] nad svojim životom.

243
00:14:49,799 --> 00:14:51,279
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže Ignacijan,

244
00:14:51,279 --> 00:14:52,039
[SPEAKER_00] lojalski,

245
00:14:52,039 --> 00:14:53,500
[SPEAKER_00] sve je u tome.

246
00:14:53,500 --> 00:14:54,639
[SPEAKER_00] Prepusti se

247
00:14:54,639 --> 00:14:56,179
[SPEAKER_00] vostvo duha sve i toga.

248
00:14:56,179 --> 00:14:57,720
[SPEAKER_00] Ali treba do toga doći.

249
00:14:57,720 --> 00:14:59,840
[SPEAKER_01] Naime, u svom povijesnom periodu,

250
00:14:59,840 --> 00:15:00,779
[SPEAKER_01] crkva je bila objelježena

251
00:15:00,779 --> 00:15:02,360
[SPEAKER_01] tom teologijom krštenja.

252
00:15:02,360 --> 00:15:03,899
[SPEAKER_01] Katekumeni su bili

253
00:15:03,899 --> 00:15:04,620
[SPEAKER_01] ti koji su

254
00:15:04,620 --> 00:15:05,240
[SPEAKER_01] vazmjena noći

255
00:15:05,240 --> 00:15:06,279
[SPEAKER_01] primali sakrament,

256
00:15:06,279 --> 00:15:06,899
[SPEAKER_01] dakle,

257
00:15:06,899 --> 00:15:08,320
[SPEAKER_01] kršćanske inicijacije.

258
00:15:08,320 --> 00:15:10,220
[SPEAKER_01] Biste li nam mogli

259
00:15:10,220 --> 00:15:11,440
[SPEAKER_01] pojasniti te običaje,

260
00:15:11,440 --> 00:15:13,220
[SPEAKER_01] zašto o tome više ne razgovaramo,

261
00:15:14,820 --> 00:15:15,379
[SPEAKER_01] povijest?

262
00:15:15,379 --> 00:15:15,820
[SPEAKER_00] Pa,

263
00:15:15,820 --> 00:15:17,080
[SPEAKER_00] prvi stoljeća

264
00:15:17,080 --> 00:15:18,100
[SPEAKER_00] bio je jako razvijen

265
00:15:18,100 --> 00:15:19,419
[SPEAKER_00] taj katekumenat

266
00:15:19,419 --> 00:15:21,679
[SPEAKER_00] i nije bilo baš lako

267
00:15:21,679 --> 00:15:23,039
[SPEAKER_00] postati kršćanin.

268
00:15:23,039 --> 00:15:25,899
[SPEAKER_00] Prvo je trebao netko,

269
00:15:25,899 --> 00:15:27,460
[SPEAKER_00] prvo kršćani su bili

270
00:15:27,460 --> 00:15:29,100
[SPEAKER_00] od početka,

271
00:15:29,100 --> 00:15:29,399
[SPEAKER_00] recimo,

272
00:15:29,399 --> 00:15:30,080
[SPEAKER_00] untar židovstva,

273
00:15:30,080 --> 00:15:30,759
[SPEAKER_00] percipirani

274
00:15:30,759 --> 00:15:31,960
[SPEAKER_00] kao jedna sekta.

275
00:15:31,960 --> 00:15:33,340
[SPEAKER_00] I bili su,

276
00:15:33,340 --> 00:15:34,860
[SPEAKER_00] znamo iz dijela apostolskih,

277
00:15:34,860 --> 00:15:35,539
[SPEAKER_00] progonjeni.

278
00:15:35,539 --> 00:15:36,399
[SPEAKER_00] Pavao ih je

279
00:15:36,399 --> 00:15:37,320
[SPEAKER_00] čak u okovima,

280
00:15:37,320 --> 00:15:38,740
[SPEAKER_00] bacao u zatvor

281
00:15:38,740 --> 00:15:39,879
[SPEAKER_00] i vodio Jeruzalem

282
00:15:39,879 --> 00:15:40,620
[SPEAKER_00] da ih se kazini

283
00:15:40,620 --> 00:15:41,580
[SPEAKER_00] ako se ne odreću vjere

284
00:15:41,580 --> 00:15:42,159
[SPEAKER_00] i tako dalje.

285
00:15:42,159 --> 00:15:43,320
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

286
00:15:43,320 --> 00:15:44,179
[SPEAKER_00] untar židovstva

287
00:15:44,179 --> 00:15:45,179
[SPEAKER_00] iz početka su bili

288
00:15:45,179 --> 00:15:45,820
[SPEAKER_00] precipirani

289
00:15:45,820 --> 00:15:46,940
[SPEAKER_00] kao jedna sekta,

290
00:15:46,940 --> 00:15:47,980
[SPEAKER_00] no kako se

291
00:15:47,980 --> 00:15:50,879
[SPEAKER_00] kršćanska poruka

292
00:15:50,879 --> 00:15:52,240
[SPEAKER_00] prelijeva

293
00:15:52,240 --> 00:15:52,980
[SPEAKER_00] ili pretače

294
00:15:52,980 --> 00:15:54,019
[SPEAKER_00] iz židovskog

295
00:15:54,019 --> 00:15:54,980
[SPEAKER_00] u grški svijet,

296
00:15:54,980 --> 00:15:55,399
[SPEAKER_00] postaju

297
00:15:55,399 --> 00:15:56,100
[SPEAKER_00] najprije

298
00:15:56,100 --> 00:15:57,240
[SPEAKER_00] mnogi prozeliti,

299
00:15:57,240 --> 00:15:58,460
[SPEAKER_00] oni koji su tragali

300
00:15:58,460 --> 00:15:59,019
[SPEAKER_00] za istinu,

301
00:15:59,019 --> 00:15:59,679
[SPEAKER_00] bogobojazni,

302
00:15:59,679 --> 00:16:00,240
[SPEAKER_00] kako ih naziva

303
00:16:00,240 --> 00:16:00,879
[SPEAKER_00] sve to pismo,

304
00:16:00,879 --> 00:16:02,360
[SPEAKER_00] oni postaju kršćani.

305
00:16:05,299 --> 00:16:06,679
[SPEAKER_00] ali još uvijek su

306
00:16:06,679 --> 00:16:08,779
[SPEAKER_00] jako zatvorene zajednice

307
00:16:08,779 --> 00:16:10,679
[SPEAKER_00] i promatrajući

308
00:16:10,679 --> 00:16:11,600
[SPEAKER_00] i njihov život,

309
00:16:11,600 --> 00:16:12,440
[SPEAKER_00] to je bilo jedna,

310
00:16:12,440 --> 00:16:13,259
[SPEAKER_00] mislim da je

311
00:16:13,259 --> 00:16:14,559
[SPEAKER_00] Tartulijan to zapisao

312
00:16:14,559 --> 00:16:15,639
[SPEAKER_00] ili je bio kod

313
00:16:15,639 --> 00:16:16,820
[SPEAKER_00] pogana

314
00:16:16,820 --> 00:16:17,759
[SPEAKER_00] jedan uzvik,

315
00:16:17,759 --> 00:16:18,139
[SPEAKER_00] dakle,

316
00:16:18,139 --> 00:16:18,919
[SPEAKER_00] kršćani su mijenjali

317
00:16:18,919 --> 00:16:19,940
[SPEAKER_00] svoj način života

318
00:16:19,940 --> 00:16:22,799
[SPEAKER_00] i to su pogani primijetili,

319
00:16:22,799 --> 00:16:23,019
[SPEAKER_00] kaže,

320
00:16:23,019 --> 00:16:24,580
[SPEAKER_00] gled kako se kršćani ljube

321
00:16:24,580 --> 00:16:26,580
[SPEAKER_00] i ta djelatna ljuba,

322
00:16:26,580 --> 00:16:27,279
[SPEAKER_00] konkretna ljuba

323
00:16:27,279 --> 00:16:28,659
[SPEAKER_00] bila je izazov za pogane.

324
00:16:28,659 --> 00:16:30,299
[SPEAKER_00] I onda bi neko nekoga znao,

325
00:16:30,299 --> 00:16:31,080
[SPEAKER_00] nekog rođaka,

326
00:16:31,080 --> 00:16:32,039
[SPEAKER_00] nekog prijatelja,

327
00:16:32,039 --> 00:16:32,220
[SPEAKER_00] kaže,

328
00:16:32,220 --> 00:16:33,159
[SPEAKER_00] pa vidi kako,

329
00:16:35,299 --> 00:16:36,340
[SPEAKER_00] mogao biti.

330
00:16:36,340 --> 00:16:38,299
[SPEAKER_00] I neko je odrastao,

331
00:16:38,299 --> 00:16:39,940
[SPEAKER_00] morao preporučiti

332
00:16:39,940 --> 00:16:41,720
[SPEAKER_00] onoga ko traži krštenje

333
00:16:41,720 --> 00:16:42,500
[SPEAKER_00] da bude kršten.

334
00:16:42,500 --> 00:16:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jedan s preporukom

335
00:16:44,000 --> 00:16:45,600
[SPEAKER_00] je mogao ući u katekumenat.

336
00:16:45,600 --> 00:16:46,860
[SPEAKER_00] S preporukom.

337
00:16:46,860 --> 00:16:47,980
[SPEAKER_00] Dobrom preporukom.

338
00:16:47,980 --> 00:16:49,059
[SPEAKER_00] To je uloga kuma.

339
00:16:49,059 --> 00:16:51,259
[SPEAKER_00] Kum jamči za njega

340
00:16:51,259 --> 00:16:52,559
[SPEAKER_00] da će biti dobar kršćanin.

341
00:16:52,559 --> 00:16:54,820
[SPEAKER_00] I kad se on prijavio

342
00:16:54,820 --> 00:16:56,799
[SPEAKER_00] da želi primiti posta kršćanin,

343
00:16:56,799 --> 00:16:58,340
[SPEAKER_00] onda je slijedila priprava

344
00:16:58,340 --> 00:16:59,159
[SPEAKER_00] katekumenata

345
00:16:59,159 --> 00:17:00,940
[SPEAKER_00] koja je trajala nekad godinu,

346
00:17:00,940 --> 00:17:01,659
[SPEAKER_00] nekad dvije godine,

347
00:17:01,659 --> 00:17:02,980
[SPEAKER_00] ovisno od situacije,

348
00:17:02,980 --> 00:17:03,899
[SPEAKER_00] ovisno od osoba.

349
00:17:04,720 --> 00:17:06,599
[SPEAKER_00] Svakako jedna ozbiljna priprava

350
00:17:06,599 --> 00:17:08,119
[SPEAKER_00] gdje se preko kateheza

351
00:17:08,119 --> 00:17:09,819
[SPEAKER_00] uvodilo kršćansku vjeru,

352
00:17:09,819 --> 00:17:11,740
[SPEAKER_00] učilo ih je ne samo

353
00:17:11,740 --> 00:17:12,819
[SPEAKER_00] da nauči nešto na pamet,

354
00:17:12,819 --> 00:17:14,599
[SPEAKER_00] nego i kršćanski način življanja.

355
00:17:14,599 --> 00:17:15,660
[SPEAKER_00] Oni su morali već

356
00:17:15,660 --> 00:17:17,240
[SPEAKER_00] i onda unapri pokazati,

357
00:17:17,240 --> 00:17:18,220
[SPEAKER_00] su spremni prihvatiti,

358
00:17:18,220 --> 00:17:19,099
[SPEAKER_00] promijeniti život,

359
00:17:19,099 --> 00:17:20,539
[SPEAKER_00] prihvatiti kršćansku poruku

360
00:17:20,539 --> 00:17:23,259
[SPEAKER_00] i kad je starješena zajednice,

361
00:17:23,259 --> 00:17:24,599
[SPEAKER_00] prezbitir ili biskup,

362
00:17:24,599 --> 00:17:25,539
[SPEAKER_00] kad su ocijenili da su

363
00:17:25,539 --> 00:17:27,299
[SPEAKER_00] dostatno opremljeni,

364
00:17:27,299 --> 00:17:28,160
[SPEAKER_00] osposobljeni,

365
00:17:28,160 --> 00:17:29,019
[SPEAKER_00] pripravni,

366
00:17:29,019 --> 00:17:30,359
[SPEAKER_00] onda se u vazbrenje noće

367
00:17:30,359 --> 00:17:31,500
[SPEAKER_00] redovito bi se krstili,

368
00:17:31,500 --> 00:17:33,420
[SPEAKER_00] dobili bi na izlasku

369
00:17:33,420 --> 00:17:34,599
[SPEAKER_00] iz krsnog zdajenica

370
00:17:34,599 --> 00:17:35,660
[SPEAKER_00] bijele haljine

371
00:17:35,660 --> 00:17:37,039
[SPEAKER_00] kao znak novosti života

372
00:17:37,039 --> 00:17:38,180
[SPEAKER_00] koji je sada darovan

373
00:17:38,180 --> 00:17:39,200
[SPEAKER_00] sa porukom

374
00:17:39,200 --> 00:17:40,400
[SPEAKER_00] da čuvaju bijelinu

375
00:17:40,400 --> 00:17:41,880
[SPEAKER_00] te haljine neokaljanom.

376
00:17:41,880 --> 00:17:42,980
[SPEAKER_00] I to je danas ostalo

377
00:17:42,980 --> 00:17:43,940
[SPEAKER_00] u krštenju djece,

378
00:17:43,940 --> 00:17:45,980
[SPEAKER_00] da čuvaju tu haljinu neokaljanom.

379
00:17:46,240 --> 00:17:48,960
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da je u prva stoljeća

380
00:17:48,960 --> 00:17:51,240
[SPEAKER_00] to je bilo vrlo, vrlo važan

381
00:17:51,240 --> 00:17:52,859
[SPEAKER_00] institut u životu crkve,

382
00:17:52,859 --> 00:17:56,559
[SPEAKER_00] no sa slobodom,

383
00:17:56,559 --> 00:17:59,140
[SPEAKER_00] sa Konstantinovim ediktom,

384
00:17:59,140 --> 00:18:00,180
[SPEAKER_00] milanskim ediktom,

385
00:18:00,180 --> 00:18:01,859
[SPEAKER_00] kad kršćani postaju slobodniji,

386
00:18:01,859 --> 00:18:03,460
[SPEAKER_00] osobito kad postaje državna religija

387
00:18:03,460 --> 00:18:04,299
[SPEAKER_00] sa teodozijem,

388
00:18:04,299 --> 00:18:05,940
[SPEAKER_00] tada praktički postaju,

389
00:18:05,940 --> 00:18:08,519
[SPEAKER_00] ulazi se na neki način

390
00:18:08,519 --> 00:18:09,960
[SPEAKER_00] rekao i bez kriterija.

391
00:18:09,960 --> 00:18:12,079
[SPEAKER_00] Ljudi se masovno okrštavaju

392
00:18:12,079 --> 00:18:13,319
[SPEAKER_00] i kako se povećao

393
00:18:13,319 --> 00:18:14,799
[SPEAKER_00] jako broj kršćana,

394
00:18:15,119 --> 00:18:16,359
[SPEAKER_00] tako se snizila i razina

395
00:18:16,359 --> 00:18:17,359
[SPEAKER_00] kršćanskog života.

396
00:18:17,359 --> 00:18:19,039
[SPEAKER_00] I to će onda dovesti

397
00:18:19,039 --> 00:18:21,259
[SPEAKER_00] opet do razvoja prakse.

398
00:18:21,259 --> 00:18:22,839
[SPEAKER_00] Bilo je pitanje

399
00:18:22,839 --> 00:18:24,059
[SPEAKER_00] što kada čovjek sagriješi.

400
00:18:24,059 --> 00:18:26,240
[SPEAKER_00] Tertulina je rekao

401
00:18:26,240 --> 00:18:27,220
[SPEAKER_00] a ništa, nije više kršćan,

402
00:18:27,220 --> 00:18:27,759
[SPEAKER_00] otpavao je.

403
00:18:27,759 --> 00:18:29,299
[SPEAKER_00] Crkva pa ne može tako,

404
00:18:29,299 --> 00:18:30,299
[SPEAKER_00] to je predstrogo,

405
00:18:30,299 --> 00:18:31,279
[SPEAKER_00] to je predzahtjevno.

406
00:18:31,279 --> 00:18:32,180
[SPEAKER_00] Ljudi su slabi,

407
00:18:32,180 --> 00:18:33,559
[SPEAKER_00] ljudi inako u prištenju mogu pasiti.

408
00:18:33,559 --> 00:18:34,880
[SPEAKER_00] I to je onda uvjetovalo

409
00:18:34,880 --> 00:18:36,240
[SPEAKER_00] razvoj sakramenta pokore.

410
00:18:36,240 --> 00:18:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] Iz početka tu bilo jako strogo.

411
00:18:38,000 --> 00:18:39,319
[SPEAKER_00] Bili su neke grijeze

412
00:18:39,319 --> 00:18:40,799
[SPEAKER_00] koji su izopćavali crkve,

413
00:18:45,119 --> 00:18:45,940
[SPEAKER_00] do kraja života.

414
00:18:45,940 --> 00:18:47,779
[SPEAKER_00] I tek bi na kraju života

415
00:18:47,779 --> 00:18:49,500
[SPEAKER_00] na neki način dobili pomirenje.

416
00:18:49,500 --> 00:18:51,339
[SPEAKER_00] Sa Kolumbanom je,

417
00:18:51,339 --> 00:18:52,460
[SPEAKER_00] svjetim Kolumbanom,

418
00:18:52,460 --> 00:18:53,759
[SPEAKER_00] ta praksa je malo ublažena,

419
00:18:53,759 --> 00:18:55,539
[SPEAKER_00] pa se je počelo malo raditi

420
00:18:55,539 --> 00:18:56,859
[SPEAKER_00] pokornička praksa,

421
00:18:56,859 --> 00:18:57,460
[SPEAKER_00] hodočašća,

422
00:18:57,460 --> 00:18:58,660
[SPEAKER_00] ajde napravi hodočašće,

423
00:18:58,660 --> 00:19:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] učini ta i ta dijela,

424
00:19:00,000 --> 00:19:01,980
[SPEAKER_00] redoviti je bila pokornička hodočašća.

425
00:19:01,980 --> 00:19:03,220
[SPEAKER_00] I onda po povratku

426
00:19:03,220 --> 00:19:04,700
[SPEAKER_00] bi dobivali od rješenja.

427
00:19:04,700 --> 00:19:05,859
[SPEAKER_00] I to je onda, eto,

428
00:19:05,859 --> 00:19:07,500
[SPEAKER_00] dalje tekao razvoj,

429
00:19:07,579 --> 00:19:09,839
[SPEAKER_00] praktički tek sredinom

430
00:19:09,839 --> 00:19:10,599
[SPEAKER_00] srednjeg vijeka,

431
00:19:10,599 --> 00:19:12,079
[SPEAKER_00] sa Tomom Akvinskim

432
00:19:12,079 --> 00:19:13,700
[SPEAKER_00] imamo dobro usustavljan

433
00:19:13,700 --> 00:19:16,079
[SPEAKER_00] razvijen na oko sakramentu pokore,

434
00:19:16,079 --> 00:19:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] koji se nužno praktički razvija

435
00:19:18,000 --> 00:19:19,460
[SPEAKER_00] i sakramentu kreštenja.

436
00:19:19,460 --> 00:19:21,579
[SPEAKER_01] Sad ste spomenuli pokoru,

437
00:19:21,579 --> 00:19:23,799
[SPEAKER_01] želi bi samo naglasiti

438
00:19:23,799 --> 00:19:26,740
[SPEAKER_01] važnost ispovjedi o ovom periodu.

439
00:19:26,740 --> 00:19:28,900
[SPEAKER_01] Što biste sad savjetovali nekome,

440
00:19:28,900 --> 00:19:30,400
[SPEAKER_01] ko vam dođe na razgovor

441
00:19:30,400 --> 00:19:31,539
[SPEAKER_01] i da vas pita kako se sad

442
00:19:31,539 --> 00:19:32,759
[SPEAKER_01] probližite ovom otajstu

443
00:19:32,759 --> 00:19:33,599
[SPEAKER_01] Kristove muke,

444
00:19:33,599 --> 00:19:35,019
[SPEAKER_01] kako mi ona može pomoći

445
00:19:35,019 --> 00:19:36,359
[SPEAKER_01] da ja nosim svoj križ?

446
00:19:36,359 --> 00:19:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da, to su sad dva pitanja.

447
00:19:38,000 --> 00:19:39,940
[SPEAKER_00] Pitanje jedno je nosenje križa,

448
00:19:39,940 --> 00:19:41,200
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno uloga patnje

449
00:19:41,200 --> 00:19:42,200
[SPEAKER_00] ili prisutnost patnje

450
00:19:42,200 --> 00:19:42,880
[SPEAKER_00] u ljudskom životu,

451
00:19:42,880 --> 00:19:43,680
[SPEAKER_00] koja je nezbiježna

452
00:19:43,680 --> 00:19:44,660
[SPEAKER_00] u jednom drugom obliku,

453
00:19:44,660 --> 00:19:46,319
[SPEAKER_00] a drugo pitanje praktički

454
00:19:46,319 --> 00:19:47,279
[SPEAKER_00] maka su povezana,

455
00:19:47,279 --> 00:19:48,359
[SPEAKER_00] to je pitanje sakramenta

456
00:19:48,359 --> 00:19:49,319
[SPEAKER_00] pomirjenja i pokore,

457
00:19:49,319 --> 00:19:50,519
[SPEAKER_00] počneći s ovim drugim.

458
00:19:50,519 --> 00:19:52,440
[SPEAKER_00] Kroz ovom korizmenom hodu

459
00:19:52,440 --> 00:19:55,039
[SPEAKER_00] crkva uči da će korizmeni,

460
00:19:55,039 --> 00:19:56,059
[SPEAKER_00] da bi bilo lijepo

461
00:19:56,059 --> 00:19:58,539
[SPEAKER_00] kada bi u pojedinačnom korizmenom hodu

462
00:19:58,539 --> 00:20:00,660
[SPEAKER_00] taj hod pred sam uskrs,

463
00:20:00,660 --> 00:20:01,799
[SPEAKER_00] oće li biti dan, dva, tri,

464
00:20:01,799 --> 00:20:02,680
[SPEAKER_00] manje važno,

465
00:20:02,680 --> 00:20:05,059
[SPEAKER_00] bio okrunjen sakramentom

466
00:20:05,059 --> 00:20:06,099
[SPEAKER_00] pomirjenja i pokore.

467
00:20:06,099 --> 00:20:09,480
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, korizmen mi treba

468
00:20:09,480 --> 00:20:11,339
[SPEAKER_00] otkriti u biti da sam slab,

469
00:20:11,339 --> 00:20:13,140
[SPEAKER_00] ali mi također otkriva

470
00:20:13,140 --> 00:20:14,079
[SPEAKER_00] da me Bog ljubi.

471
00:20:14,079 --> 00:20:18,799
[SPEAKER_00] Možda je,

472
00:20:18,799 --> 00:20:20,339
[SPEAKER_00] jako je važno,

473
00:20:20,339 --> 00:20:22,200
[SPEAKER_00] tijel sreć možda nije suvišno,

474
00:20:22,200 --> 00:20:23,480
[SPEAKER_00] ali jako je važno spomenuti

475
00:20:23,480 --> 00:20:25,579
[SPEAKER_00] kako je prva gospodina riječ,

476
00:20:25,579 --> 00:20:26,460
[SPEAKER_00] kako je Marko bilježno

477
00:20:26,460 --> 00:20:27,180
[SPEAKER_00] svom evanđelju,

478
00:20:27,180 --> 00:20:28,480
[SPEAKER_00] poziv na obraćenje.

479
00:20:28,480 --> 00:20:30,319
[SPEAKER_00] Ispuno se vrijeme,

480
00:20:30,319 --> 00:20:32,200
[SPEAKER_00] približno se kraljevstvo Božije,

481
00:20:32,200 --> 00:20:33,559
[SPEAKER_00] obratite se

482
00:20:33,559 --> 00:20:35,359
[SPEAKER_00] i vjerojte evanđelju.

483
00:20:35,359 --> 00:20:37,140
[SPEAKER_00] Obratite se.

484
00:20:37,140 --> 00:20:38,319
[SPEAKER_00] U drugim riječima,

485
00:20:38,319 --> 00:20:39,279
[SPEAKER_00] gospodine,

486
00:20:39,279 --> 00:20:40,160
[SPEAKER_00] kad nas poziva

487
00:20:40,160 --> 00:20:41,640
[SPEAKER_00] da postanemo njegove učenici,

488
00:20:41,640 --> 00:20:43,720
[SPEAKER_00] to je ujedno poziv na obraćenje.

489
00:20:43,720 --> 00:20:45,240
[SPEAKER_00] I to bi trebao biti

490
00:20:45,240 --> 00:20:46,640
[SPEAKER_00] stil krštanskog života.

491
00:20:46,640 --> 00:20:49,059
[SPEAKER_00] Obraćenje nije pitanje

492
00:20:49,059 --> 00:20:50,440
[SPEAKER_00] jednog trenutka, jednog dana,

493
00:20:51,079 --> 00:20:52,799
[SPEAKER_00] nego stil življenja

494
00:20:52,799 --> 00:20:55,380
[SPEAKER_00] uvijek mogu biti više Božiji,

495
00:20:55,380 --> 00:20:58,279
[SPEAKER_00] uvijek mogu biti bolji,

496
00:20:58,279 --> 00:20:59,980
[SPEAKER_00] čestitiji, plemenitiji,

497
00:20:59,980 --> 00:21:01,019
[SPEAKER_00] istinitiji.

498
00:21:01,019 --> 00:21:02,839
[SPEAKER_00] I na tome korizma

499
00:21:02,839 --> 00:21:04,579
[SPEAKER_00] me na taj put stavlja.

500
00:21:04,579 --> 00:21:07,299
[SPEAKER_00] Otkriva svoje nekako

501
00:21:07,299 --> 00:21:09,460
[SPEAKER_00] poteškoće,

502
00:21:09,460 --> 00:21:10,359
[SPEAKER_00] svoje nedostatke,

503
00:21:10,359 --> 00:21:11,140
[SPEAKER_00] svoje mane,

504
00:21:11,140 --> 00:21:12,779
[SPEAKER_00] jednim pogledom,

505
00:21:12,779 --> 00:21:14,220
[SPEAKER_00] introspektivnim pogledom,

506
00:21:14,220 --> 00:21:16,519
[SPEAKER_00] koji neće biti samo osuđujući,

507
00:21:16,519 --> 00:21:18,019
[SPEAKER_00] nego neki način taj pogled

508
00:21:18,019 --> 00:21:19,460
[SPEAKER_00] istodobno je usmeren

509
00:21:19,460 --> 00:21:20,500
[SPEAKER_00] prema Kristovu križu

510
00:21:20,500 --> 00:21:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] koji kaže

511
00:21:21,000 --> 00:21:23,839
[SPEAKER_00] ali Bog te u tvojim slabostima ljubi.

512
00:21:23,839 --> 00:21:25,819
[SPEAKER_00] Bog ti podiže na noge.

513
00:21:25,819 --> 00:21:27,119
[SPEAKER_00] Bog ti pruža ruku.

514
00:21:27,119 --> 00:21:29,460
[SPEAKER_00] I taj proces obraćenja,

515
00:21:29,460 --> 00:21:31,119
[SPEAKER_00] on svoju krunu ima

516
00:21:31,119 --> 00:21:32,779
[SPEAKER_00] u sakramentu pomirenja i pokore.

517
00:21:32,779 --> 00:21:34,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam napisal jedan članak

518
00:21:34,619 --> 00:21:38,339
[SPEAKER_00] da je sakramentu pomirenja i pokore

519
00:21:38,339 --> 00:21:39,319
[SPEAKER_00] Božji zagrljaj.

520
00:21:39,319 --> 00:21:41,119
[SPEAKER_00] To je ući u Božji zagrljaj.

521
00:21:41,119 --> 00:21:42,359
[SPEAKER_00] Bog me čeka

522
00:21:42,359 --> 00:21:44,740
[SPEAKER_00] u tom procesu obraćenja

523
00:21:44,740 --> 00:21:46,299
[SPEAKER_00] kada ja spoznajem kakav sam,

524
00:21:46,299 --> 00:21:49,119
[SPEAKER_00] ja shvaćam da me Bog u moje slabosti ljubi,

525
00:21:49,119 --> 00:21:50,900
[SPEAKER_00] da me prijima u svoj zagrljaj,

526
00:21:50,920 --> 00:21:52,660
[SPEAKER_00] briše ništi moje grijehe,

527
00:21:52,660 --> 00:21:54,460
[SPEAKER_00] a ljubi mene svoje dijete.

528
00:21:54,460 --> 00:21:56,420
[SPEAKER_00] Zato je to nešto,

529
00:21:56,420 --> 00:21:57,920
[SPEAKER_00] osob za nas svećenike,

530
00:21:57,920 --> 00:22:00,700
[SPEAKER_00] redovito smo ganuti, dirnuti,

531
00:22:00,700 --> 00:22:04,079
[SPEAKER_00] kad služimo sakramentu pomirenja i pokore,

532
00:22:04,079 --> 00:22:05,619
[SPEAKER_00] osob da kad doživimo da

533
00:22:05,619 --> 00:22:08,119
[SPEAKER_00] ljudi sa teškim teretima grijeha,

534
00:22:08,119 --> 00:22:09,819
[SPEAKER_00] koji se možda nisu spovedili godinama,

535
00:22:09,819 --> 00:22:11,039
[SPEAKER_00] kao u tom procesu,

536
00:22:11,039 --> 00:22:12,720
[SPEAKER_00] korizmenom promišljanja

537
00:22:12,720 --> 00:22:14,319
[SPEAKER_00] i dođu taknuti Božijom milošću,

538
00:22:14,319 --> 00:22:16,619
[SPEAKER_00] da dođu do odluke,

539
00:22:16,619 --> 00:22:18,940
[SPEAKER_00] da se žele vratiti u očev zagrljaj.

540
00:22:18,940 --> 00:22:22,039
[SPEAKER_00] To je jako odvjeljivo.

541
00:22:22,039 --> 00:22:24,180
[SPEAKER_00] S tog aspekta,

542
00:22:24,180 --> 00:22:25,579
[SPEAKER_00] rekao bih,

543
00:22:25,579 --> 00:22:27,940
[SPEAKER_00] da bi korizma

544
00:22:27,940 --> 00:22:29,539
[SPEAKER_00] sauvisio od osobe do osobe,

545
00:22:29,539 --> 00:22:30,819
[SPEAKER_00] ali bi ona trebala

546
00:22:30,819 --> 00:22:32,700
[SPEAKER_00] svake osobe na neki način

547
00:22:32,700 --> 00:22:35,220
[SPEAKER_00] ajde završiti sakramentu pomirenja i pokore.

548
00:22:35,700 --> 00:22:36,900
[SPEAKER_00] Možda ima koja osoba,

549
00:22:36,900 --> 00:22:38,859
[SPEAKER_00] naše bakice ili stari osoba

550
00:22:38,859 --> 00:22:40,259
[SPEAKER_00] koji se redovito ispovjedaju,

551
00:22:40,259 --> 00:22:41,799
[SPEAKER_00] pa možda svaki tjedan

552
00:22:41,799 --> 00:22:43,079
[SPEAKER_00] ili svaki petnaestak dana

553
00:22:43,079 --> 00:22:46,200
[SPEAKER_00] i koji nemoju prigodu nešto veliko sagriješiti,

554
00:22:46,200 --> 00:22:49,160
[SPEAKER_00] ali što je iskustvo brojnih,

555
00:22:49,160 --> 00:22:51,180
[SPEAKER_00] mi smo grijeh.

556
00:22:51,180 --> 00:22:53,660
[SPEAKER_00] Kad promišljamo o sebi,

557
00:22:53,660 --> 00:22:54,359
[SPEAKER_00] svom životu,

558
00:22:54,359 --> 00:22:58,079
[SPEAKER_00] kako je malo ljuba preobrazila našu nutrinu,

559
00:22:58,079 --> 00:23:01,460
[SPEAKER_00] kako ljuba ne motivira sve moje postupke,

560
00:23:01,460 --> 00:23:02,779
[SPEAKER_00] onda sam potreban,

561
00:23:02,779 --> 00:23:04,880
[SPEAKER_00] potreban sam Božijeg zagrljaja,

562
00:23:05,039 --> 00:23:05,940
[SPEAKER_00] Božijeg opraštanja,

563
00:23:05,940 --> 00:23:06,720
[SPEAKER_00] Božije ljubavi.

564
00:23:06,720 --> 00:23:10,539
[SPEAKER_00] Zato je dobro i crkva to mudro,

565
00:23:10,539 --> 00:23:11,460
[SPEAKER_00] kao mudra majka,

566
00:23:11,460 --> 00:23:12,759
[SPEAKER_00] kao dobra majka,

567
00:23:12,759 --> 00:23:15,160
[SPEAKER_00] tako i organizira korizbeni hod,

568
00:23:15,160 --> 00:23:16,500
[SPEAKER_00] da on uvijek na neki način,

569
00:23:16,500 --> 00:23:17,720
[SPEAKER_00] pred neposledno pred uskrs,

570
00:23:17,720 --> 00:23:20,319
[SPEAKER_00] on nudi i mogućnost Božijeg zagrljaja

571
00:23:20,319 --> 00:23:21,920
[SPEAKER_00] u sakramentu pomirenja i pokore.

572
00:23:21,920 --> 00:23:23,099
[SPEAKER_00] Danas ona, dragi Bog,

573
00:23:23,099 --> 00:23:24,299
[SPEAKER_00] podigne na noge i kaže,

574
00:23:24,299 --> 00:23:26,099
[SPEAKER_00] ajde, volim te,

575
00:23:26,099 --> 00:23:27,579
[SPEAKER_00] idi naprijed.

576
00:23:27,579 --> 00:23:29,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo drugo pitanje

577
00:23:29,380 --> 00:23:30,799
[SPEAKER_00] koje je povezano s ovim prvim

578
00:23:30,799 --> 00:23:31,900
[SPEAKER_00] je pitanje patnje.

579
00:23:31,900 --> 00:23:33,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ono je jako bremenito

580
00:23:34,380 --> 00:23:36,299
[SPEAKER_00] da nema praktički obitelji,

581
00:23:36,299 --> 00:23:38,220
[SPEAKER_00] nema odrasle osobe za djecu,

582
00:23:38,220 --> 00:23:39,180
[SPEAKER_00] ajde, neću reći,

583
00:23:39,180 --> 00:23:41,079
[SPEAKER_00] da nema neki vlasti križ,

584
00:23:41,079 --> 00:23:43,319
[SPEAKER_00] osobni, obiteljski,

585
00:23:43,319 --> 00:23:46,259
[SPEAKER_00] je li to križ nezaposlenosti,

586
00:23:46,259 --> 00:23:47,940
[SPEAKER_00] je li to križ možda siromaštva,

587
00:23:47,940 --> 00:23:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] je li to križ poremećenih odnosa,

588
00:23:50,000 --> 00:23:52,900
[SPEAKER_00] je li to križ neke vrste obisnosti.

589
00:23:53,960 --> 00:23:57,279
[SPEAKER_00] Najčešće je izmiješano puno toga,

590
00:23:57,279 --> 00:23:59,119
[SPEAKER_00] puno je tih situacija izmiješano,

591
00:23:59,119 --> 00:24:01,599
[SPEAKER_00] ono što nazivamo križ jedne obitelji,

592
00:24:01,599 --> 00:24:02,880
[SPEAKER_00] križ jedne osobe.

593
00:24:02,880 --> 00:24:06,420
[SPEAKER_00] Pod križe možemo praktički

594
00:24:06,420 --> 00:24:09,259
[SPEAKER_00] shvatiti sve ono što osobu

595
00:24:09,259 --> 00:24:09,799
[SPEAKER_00] ugrožava,

596
00:24:09,799 --> 00:24:11,640
[SPEAKER_00] što je mrvi,

597
00:24:11,640 --> 00:24:13,799
[SPEAKER_00] što ugrožava njezinu životnu,

598
00:24:13,799 --> 00:24:15,559
[SPEAKER_00] rad oživljenja,

599
00:24:15,559 --> 00:24:17,680
[SPEAKER_00] to možemo precipirati kao križ.

600
00:24:17,680 --> 00:24:19,119
[SPEAKER_00] To mogu biti različite,

601
00:24:19,119 --> 00:24:20,319
[SPEAKER_00] stvari što sam nabrojio.

602
00:24:20,319 --> 00:24:22,640
[SPEAKER_00] E sa kako se tu postaviti?

603
00:24:22,640 --> 00:24:27,019
[SPEAKER_00] Ljudi redovito,

604
00:24:27,019 --> 00:24:28,299
[SPEAKER_00] naravno, da će se boriti

605
00:24:28,299 --> 00:24:30,400
[SPEAKER_00] da pobjede tu situaciju,

606
00:24:30,400 --> 00:24:31,559
[SPEAKER_00] ako je riječ na jedan pojma

607
00:24:31,559 --> 00:24:32,380
[SPEAKER_00] o nezaposlenosti,

608
00:24:32,380 --> 00:24:33,299
[SPEAKER_00] da nađu zaposlenje,

609
00:24:33,299 --> 00:24:34,420
[SPEAKER_00] ako je riječ o bolesti,

610
00:24:34,420 --> 00:24:35,180
[SPEAKER_00] da idu u bolnicu,

611
00:24:35,180 --> 00:24:36,440
[SPEAKER_00] traže pomoć od liječnika,

612
00:24:36,440 --> 00:24:37,259
[SPEAKER_00] sve.

613
00:24:37,259 --> 00:24:38,819
[SPEAKER_00] Ali mislim da je jako važno

614
00:24:38,819 --> 00:24:40,319
[SPEAKER_00] u toj situaciji,

615
00:24:40,319 --> 00:24:41,759
[SPEAKER_00] koju nazvamo situacija križa,

616
00:24:41,759 --> 00:24:43,019
[SPEAKER_00] jednim teološkim govorom,

617
00:24:43,799 --> 00:24:45,740
[SPEAKER_00] situacija životnih lomova,

618
00:24:45,740 --> 00:24:47,019
[SPEAKER_00] da je jako važno

619
00:24:47,019 --> 00:24:48,859
[SPEAKER_00] tu situaciju dijeliti

620
00:24:48,859 --> 00:24:50,160
[SPEAKER_00] s gospodinom Isusom.

621
00:24:50,160 --> 00:24:51,740
[SPEAKER_00] I korisbeni hod

622
00:24:51,740 --> 00:24:52,819
[SPEAKER_00] u koji nam je pred očima

623
00:24:52,819 --> 00:24:53,700
[SPEAKER_00] Kristovo križ

624
00:24:53,700 --> 00:24:54,759
[SPEAKER_00] može biti

625
00:24:54,759 --> 00:24:56,819
[SPEAKER_00] od silno velike važnosti.

626
00:24:56,819 --> 00:24:57,980
[SPEAKER_00] Može biti,

627
00:24:57,980 --> 00:24:58,700
[SPEAKER_00] ma rekao bih,

628
00:24:58,700 --> 00:24:59,980
[SPEAKER_00] izvor snage

629
00:24:59,980 --> 00:25:02,259
[SPEAKER_00] i da to što me do danas,

630
00:25:02,259 --> 00:25:03,380
[SPEAKER_00] evo što me jučer,

631
00:25:03,380 --> 00:25:03,960
[SPEAKER_00] prekučer,

632
00:25:03,960 --> 00:25:05,240
[SPEAKER_00] što me do danas smrvi,

633
00:25:05,240 --> 00:25:06,740
[SPEAKER_00] od jedan put može postati

634
00:25:06,740 --> 00:25:08,819
[SPEAKER_00] izvor snage za moj život.

635
00:25:08,819 --> 00:25:10,740
[SPEAKER_00] Ako to znam,

636
00:25:10,740 --> 00:25:11,700
[SPEAKER_00] tu situaciju,

637
00:25:11,700 --> 00:25:12,579
[SPEAKER_00] ako znam podijeliti

638
00:25:12,579 --> 00:25:13,579
[SPEAKER_00] gospodinom Isusom.

639
00:25:13,799 --> 00:25:14,079
[SPEAKER_00] Kako?

640
00:25:14,079 --> 00:25:14,740
[SPEAKER_00] Evo kako.

641
00:25:14,740 --> 00:25:15,779
[SPEAKER_00] Prvo,

642
00:25:15,779 --> 00:25:20,519
[SPEAKER_00] teološki gledano,

643
00:25:20,519 --> 00:25:22,480
[SPEAKER_00] taj križ

644
00:25:22,480 --> 00:25:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] otkriva moja ograničenja.

645
00:25:24,000 --> 00:25:25,660
[SPEAKER_00] Otkriva da ne mogu.

646
00:25:25,660 --> 00:25:27,440
[SPEAKER_00] Da ne mogu rišiti svoji problem.

647
00:25:27,440 --> 00:25:29,019
[SPEAKER_00] Je li to problem bolesti?

648
00:25:29,019 --> 00:25:30,359
[SPEAKER_00] Je li to problem narušenih odnose?

649
00:25:30,359 --> 00:25:31,299
[SPEAKER_00] Je li to problem mene,

650
00:25:31,299 --> 00:25:32,579
[SPEAKER_00] mojih nekih ovisnosti

651
00:25:32,579 --> 00:25:33,400
[SPEAKER_00] o grijecima

652
00:25:33,400 --> 00:25:34,579
[SPEAKER_00] jedne, druge, treće vrste?

653
00:25:34,579 --> 00:25:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] Vidim, zarobljavam.

654
00:25:36,000 --> 00:25:36,640
[SPEAKER_00] Ne mogu.

655
00:25:36,640 --> 00:25:38,700
[SPEAKER_00] Taj križ mi kaže,

656
00:25:38,700 --> 00:25:39,579
[SPEAKER_00] ti si ograničen.

657
00:25:40,299 --> 00:25:41,500
[SPEAKER_00] tvoje sile su ograničene.

658
00:25:41,500 --> 00:25:43,500
[SPEAKER_00] I kada ja to spoznam,

659
00:25:43,500 --> 00:25:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] gotovo instiktivno se u meni javlja

660
00:25:48,000 --> 00:25:49,839
[SPEAKER_00] jedna otvorenost prema

661
00:25:49,839 --> 00:25:51,079
[SPEAKER_00] trasedentru,

662
00:25:51,079 --> 00:25:51,980
[SPEAKER_00] prema gospodinu Bogu

663
00:25:51,980 --> 00:25:52,559
[SPEAKER_00] koji je već tu.

664
00:25:52,559 --> 00:25:55,519
[SPEAKER_00] Koji želi ući u tu situaciju.

665
00:25:55,519 --> 00:25:57,619
[SPEAKER_00] Što mi još kaže teologija,

666
00:25:57,619 --> 00:25:58,799
[SPEAKER_00] duhovna teologija,

667
00:25:58,799 --> 00:26:00,700
[SPEAKER_00] kaže da taj križ koji je došao,

668
00:26:01,900 --> 00:26:03,299
[SPEAKER_00] on nije bez Boga.

669
00:26:03,299 --> 00:26:06,559
[SPEAKER_00] Ili ga je Bog htio,

670
00:26:06,559 --> 00:26:07,859
[SPEAKER_00] ili ga je dopustio.

671
00:26:07,859 --> 00:26:10,799
[SPEAKER_00] Vjera mi kaže,

672
00:26:10,799 --> 00:26:11,640
[SPEAKER_00] sveta pismo kaže,

673
00:26:11,640 --> 00:26:12,640
[SPEAKER_00] da su mom životu,

674
00:26:12,640 --> 00:26:14,019
[SPEAKER_00] životu Božijeg djeteta,

675
00:26:14,019 --> 00:26:15,599
[SPEAKER_00] ne može dogoditi ništa

676
00:26:15,599 --> 00:26:16,779
[SPEAKER_00] što Bog ili ne želi,

677
00:26:16,779 --> 00:26:17,599
[SPEAKER_00] ili ne dopušta.

678
00:26:17,599 --> 00:26:19,119
[SPEAKER_00] A što mi još kaže Vjera?

679
00:26:19,119 --> 00:26:20,259
[SPEAKER_00] Pavlona dva mjesta rimljanima

680
00:26:20,259 --> 00:26:21,119
[SPEAKER_00] i prvom koričanima,

681
00:26:21,119 --> 00:26:23,299
[SPEAKER_00] da ako ja ostanem vjeran,

682
00:26:23,299 --> 00:26:25,140
[SPEAKER_00] srcem uspremiam gospodinu Bogu,

683
00:26:25,140 --> 00:26:27,279
[SPEAKER_00] ako ljuba prema dragom Bogu

684
00:26:27,279 --> 00:26:28,680
[SPEAKER_00] na neki način animira

685
00:26:28,680 --> 00:26:30,440
[SPEAKER_00] i moj život,

686
00:26:30,440 --> 00:26:32,339
[SPEAKER_00] i ona središa nit mog života,

687
00:26:32,339 --> 00:26:34,299
[SPEAKER_00] tada mi Božja riječ garantira

688
00:26:34,299 --> 00:26:36,579
[SPEAKER_00] da će se sve to okreni na moje dobro.

689
00:26:36,579 --> 00:26:37,980
[SPEAKER_00] Sve.

690
00:26:37,980 --> 00:26:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] Taj križ koji me je satirao,

691
00:26:41,000 --> 00:26:43,220
[SPEAKER_00] on postaje izvor moje snage

692
00:26:43,220 --> 00:26:45,279
[SPEAKER_00] kad ga ja živim sa Kristom.

693
00:26:45,279 --> 00:26:47,839
[SPEAKER_00] I to je iskustvo brojnih ljudi.

694
00:26:47,839 --> 00:26:50,119
[SPEAKER_00] Ja volim reći ljudima ovako,

695
00:26:50,119 --> 00:26:50,640
[SPEAKER_00] otprilike,

696
00:26:50,640 --> 00:26:54,420
[SPEAKER_00] križ, ta situacija kad je živite bez Krista,

697
00:26:54,420 --> 00:26:55,319
[SPEAKER_00] ona je proklestva.

698
00:26:55,319 --> 00:26:56,920
[SPEAKER_00] Ona vas mrvi, lomi.

699
00:26:57,799 --> 00:27:00,400
[SPEAKER_00] Ali kad je Krist na križu,

700
00:27:00,400 --> 00:27:01,640
[SPEAKER_00] kad je Krist,

701
00:27:01,640 --> 00:27:03,539
[SPEAKER_00] a Krist je na križu uvijek,

702
00:27:03,539 --> 00:27:06,380
[SPEAKER_00] tada ona postaje izvor blagoslova.

703
00:27:06,380 --> 00:27:09,740
[SPEAKER_00] Kad znamo tu situaciju živjeti gospodinom,

704
00:27:09,740 --> 00:27:12,319
[SPEAKER_00] mi smo svoje patnje s njim sjediniti,

705
00:27:12,319 --> 00:27:13,380
[SPEAKER_00] s njim podijeliti.

706
00:27:13,380 --> 00:27:14,559
[SPEAKER_00] A on kaže,

707
00:27:14,559 --> 00:27:15,680
[SPEAKER_00] neće vas ostaviti,

708
00:27:15,680 --> 00:27:16,359
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam s vama.

709
00:27:16,359 --> 00:27:17,799
[SPEAKER_00] Pa vonegdje kaže,

710
00:27:17,799 --> 00:27:19,940
[SPEAKER_00] neće vam se dati križ koji ne možete nositi.

711
00:27:19,940 --> 00:27:21,460
[SPEAKER_00] On ga u biti s nama nosi.

712
00:27:21,460 --> 00:27:24,259
[SPEAKER_00] Ima još nešto.

713
00:27:24,259 --> 00:27:27,680
[SPEAKER_00] Kad očima vjeri prihvatim tu situaciju križa,

714
00:27:27,799 --> 00:27:32,400
[SPEAKER_00] ovoj Kološan ima 1.9,

715
00:27:32,400 --> 00:27:33,619
[SPEAKER_00] ili 1.14,

716
00:27:33,619 --> 00:27:36,200
[SPEAKER_00] nesam siguran sad svakavkom Kološan na prvo poglavlji,

717
00:27:36,200 --> 00:27:37,519
[SPEAKER_00] kaže,

718
00:27:37,519 --> 00:27:38,099
[SPEAKER_00] Pavao,

719
00:27:38,099 --> 00:27:39,779
[SPEAKER_00] da on u svome tijelu

720
00:27:39,779 --> 00:27:41,339
[SPEAKER_00] nadopunja što nedostaje

721
00:27:41,339 --> 00:27:43,400
[SPEAKER_00] Kristovim patnjama za njegovu tijelu crkvu.

722
00:27:43,400 --> 00:27:45,220
[SPEAKER_00] A to znači,

723
00:27:45,220 --> 00:27:48,920
[SPEAKER_00] kad ja s Kristom želim podijeli svoj križ,

724
00:27:48,920 --> 00:27:50,799
[SPEAKER_00] nešto se čudesno događa.

725
00:27:51,259 --> 00:27:55,160
[SPEAKER_00] Krist računa na tu moju kapljicu patnje u oceanu,

726
00:27:55,160 --> 00:27:56,880
[SPEAKER_00] njegove patnje, njegove muke,

727
00:27:56,880 --> 00:27:58,460
[SPEAKER_00] koja je izračana njegove ljubavi,

728
00:27:58,460 --> 00:28:01,319
[SPEAKER_00] i on je uzima kao su odkupiteljsku.

729
00:28:01,319 --> 00:28:03,119
[SPEAKER_00] Ona daje neizmjernu vrijednost.

730
00:28:03,119 --> 00:28:05,359
[SPEAKER_00] Mi po toj patnji, po tom križu,

731
00:28:05,359 --> 00:28:06,599
[SPEAKER_00] koji dijelimo s Kristom,

732
00:28:06,599 --> 00:28:07,740
[SPEAKER_00] s koji s Kristom živimo,

733
00:28:08,119 --> 00:28:09,819
[SPEAKER_00] postajemo s Kristom su odkupitelji

734
00:28:09,819 --> 00:28:11,500
[SPEAKER_00] u procesu odkupljenja.

735
00:28:11,500 --> 00:28:14,180
[SPEAKER_00] To je nešto veličanstveno,

736
00:28:14,180 --> 00:28:15,900
[SPEAKER_00] nešto neizmjerno.

737
00:28:15,900 --> 00:28:18,680
[SPEAKER_00] I to bi trebalo motivirati

738
00:28:18,680 --> 00:28:19,640
[SPEAKER_00] nas kršćane,

739
00:28:19,640 --> 00:28:21,759
[SPEAKER_00] kad se dogodi bilo koji oblik križa,

740
00:28:21,759 --> 00:28:24,900
[SPEAKER_00] da mirno, mirno to prihvatim.

741
00:28:24,900 --> 00:28:26,960
[SPEAKER_00] I znajući da nisam sam,

742
00:28:26,960 --> 00:28:27,940
[SPEAKER_00] da je dragi Bog tu,

743
00:28:27,940 --> 00:28:29,819
[SPEAKER_00] i da tu moju patnju

744
00:28:29,819 --> 00:28:31,240
[SPEAKER_00] on praktički preobražava

745
00:28:31,240 --> 00:28:32,339
[SPEAKER_00] u izvor blagoslova

746
00:28:32,339 --> 00:28:34,960
[SPEAKER_00] i praktički doprinosim

747
00:28:34,960 --> 00:28:36,880
[SPEAKER_00] dijelu Kristova odkupljenja.

748
00:28:37,400 --> 00:28:38,779
[SPEAKER_00] Kako bi ovo moglo promijeniti,

749
00:28:38,779 --> 00:28:39,700
[SPEAKER_00] obogatiti života,

750
00:28:39,700 --> 00:28:42,240
[SPEAKER_00] recimo tolikih starica, staraca,

751
00:28:42,240 --> 00:28:46,579
[SPEAKER_00] koji žive možda u tim sami,

752
00:28:46,579 --> 00:28:47,839
[SPEAKER_00] možda po tim stanovima,

753
00:28:47,839 --> 00:28:49,599
[SPEAKER_00] odvojni od djeca,

754
00:28:49,599 --> 00:28:51,200
[SPEAKER_00] i to i boli ta situacija.

755
00:28:51,200 --> 00:28:53,359
[SPEAKER_00] Ili su možda čak i bolešću pritisnuti,

756
00:28:53,359 --> 00:28:54,660
[SPEAKER_00] ako ne bolešću, da starošću.

757
00:28:54,660 --> 00:28:57,420
[SPEAKER_00] I to može biti izvor njihova posvećenja

758
00:28:57,420 --> 00:28:59,019
[SPEAKER_00] i rekao bih izvor

759
00:28:59,019 --> 00:29:00,880
[SPEAKER_00] jedne velike duhovne snage

760
00:29:00,880 --> 00:29:01,720
[SPEAKER_00] za njihovo život.

761
00:29:01,720 --> 00:29:04,079
[SPEAKER_01] Sada kada smo još na temi ispovjede,

762
00:29:04,079 --> 00:29:06,119
[SPEAKER_01] biste li mogli dati određene smjernice?

763
00:29:06,119 --> 00:29:07,500
[SPEAKER_01] Kako se najbolje pripremi

764
00:29:07,500 --> 00:29:08,400
[SPEAKER_01] za dobru ispovjedu?

765
00:29:08,400 --> 00:29:10,240
[SPEAKER_00] A to je dobro pitanje.

766
00:29:10,240 --> 00:29:14,299
[SPEAKER_00] Redovito mi,

767
00:29:14,299 --> 00:29:15,180
[SPEAKER_00] kad dođemo,

768
00:29:15,180 --> 00:29:16,740
[SPEAKER_00] kao ono pet koraka

769
00:29:16,740 --> 00:29:17,880
[SPEAKER_00] za obaj dobro ispovjede,

770
00:29:17,880 --> 00:29:20,079
[SPEAKER_00] prvo kao promisliti svoje grijehe,

771
00:29:20,079 --> 00:29:21,940
[SPEAKER_00] dakle napraviti jedan dobar ispis savjesti,

772
00:29:21,940 --> 00:29:24,059
[SPEAKER_00] onda se za njih odlučno,

773
00:29:24,059 --> 00:29:25,200
[SPEAKER_00] čvrsto pokajati,

774
00:29:25,200 --> 00:29:26,819
[SPEAKER_00] reći ih svećeniku

775
00:29:26,819 --> 00:29:28,440
[SPEAKER_00] po broju,

776
00:29:28,440 --> 00:29:30,019
[SPEAKER_00] po težini,

777
00:29:30,019 --> 00:29:31,339
[SPEAKER_00] jesu li smrtni ili laki,

778
00:29:31,339 --> 00:29:31,940
[SPEAKER_00] ako su smrti,

779
00:29:31,940 --> 00:29:32,579
[SPEAKER_00] onda i po broju,

780
00:29:32,579 --> 00:29:33,839
[SPEAKER_00] koliko ih je puta bilo,

781
00:29:33,839 --> 00:29:37,099
[SPEAKER_00] i onda ono zadovoljstveno primito dišenje

782
00:29:37,099 --> 00:29:39,559
[SPEAKER_00] i zadovoljstveno koje je svećenik naredio,

783
00:29:39,559 --> 00:29:41,460
[SPEAKER_00] to po niznošću,

784
00:29:41,460 --> 00:29:42,779
[SPEAKER_00] zahvalnošću izvršiti.

785
00:29:43,279 --> 00:29:50,140
[SPEAKER_00] Nisu grijesi ono što obilježava moj život,

786
00:29:50,140 --> 00:29:53,559
[SPEAKER_00] ili nisu samo grijesi sadržaj mojej nutrine,

787
00:29:53,559 --> 00:29:54,259
[SPEAKER_00] mojeg srca.

788
00:29:54,259 --> 00:29:58,819
[SPEAKER_00] U tom introspektirnom pogledu

789
00:29:58,819 --> 00:30:00,339
[SPEAKER_00] na moj savjest,

790
00:30:00,339 --> 00:30:01,160
[SPEAKER_00] na moju nutrinu,

791
00:30:01,160 --> 00:30:03,119
[SPEAKER_00] ja bi trebao otkriti puno dobra.

792
00:30:03,119 --> 00:30:05,359
[SPEAKER_00] Puno dobra.

793
00:30:05,359 --> 00:30:07,200
[SPEAKER_00] Pa načinio jedno dobro,

794
00:30:07,200 --> 00:30:07,759
[SPEAKER_00] drugo dobro.

795
00:30:07,759 --> 00:30:10,619
[SPEAKER_00] I to dobro prepoznate na neki način

796
00:30:10,619 --> 00:30:11,579
[SPEAKER_00] kao Božji dar.

797
00:30:12,180 --> 00:30:14,319
[SPEAKER_00] Bog mi je dao da učinim to dobro.

798
00:30:14,319 --> 00:30:16,759
[SPEAKER_00] I onda Bogu zahvaliti za to.

799
00:30:16,759 --> 00:30:20,079
[SPEAKER_00] Bogu zahvaliti.

800
00:30:20,079 --> 00:30:22,819
[SPEAKER_00] Bogu dati hvalu za ono dobro

801
00:30:22,819 --> 00:30:24,099
[SPEAKER_00] koje je preko mene izveo

802
00:30:24,099 --> 00:30:25,599
[SPEAKER_00] možda i u mom životu,

803
00:30:25,599 --> 00:30:27,279
[SPEAKER_00] ali još više u životu drugih ljudi.

804
00:30:27,279 --> 00:30:30,059
[SPEAKER_00] I to onda pogled s mene

805
00:30:30,059 --> 00:30:32,440
[SPEAKER_00] premješta na gospodina Boga.

806
00:30:32,440 --> 00:30:33,920
[SPEAKER_00] On je u središtu.

807
00:30:33,920 --> 00:30:36,119
[SPEAKER_00] Ja se u odnosu na njega mjerim.

808
00:30:36,119 --> 00:30:39,380
[SPEAKER_00] Drugo, u tom ispitu sad grijeha,

809
00:30:39,380 --> 00:30:41,559
[SPEAKER_00] mi često puta ispovjedamo

810
00:30:41,559 --> 00:30:42,859
[SPEAKER_00] plodove.

811
00:30:42,859 --> 00:30:45,799
[SPEAKER_00] Ogovarao sam dva, tri puta.

812
00:30:45,799 --> 00:30:48,579
[SPEAKER_00] Pomizuo sam nešto ružno nekoj osobi.

813
00:30:48,579 --> 00:30:50,200
[SPEAKER_00] Rekao sam jednu psovku.

814
00:30:50,200 --> 00:30:53,200
[SPEAKER_00] Ali je temeljno pitanje zašto?

815
00:30:55,880 --> 00:30:57,339
[SPEAKER_00] Treba dublje zaveriti u srcu.

816
00:30:57,339 --> 00:30:58,900
[SPEAKER_00] Otkreti ono dominantno u srcu.

817
00:30:59,000 --> 00:31:03,819
[SPEAKER_00] čega se iz kojeg se ozračnja nutarnjeg rađaju ti plodovi koje ja ispovjedam.

818
00:31:04,140 --> 00:31:10,519
[SPEAKER_00] Ako to ne otkrijem, opet ću te plodove za cijelan dana ili za petnec dana opet ću ih ispovjediti.

819
00:31:10,980 --> 00:31:12,980
[SPEAKER_00] Treba korijenja iščupati.

820
00:31:12,980 --> 00:31:16,240
[SPEAKER_00] A redobito je korijenje u biti sebe ljublje.

821
00:31:16,759 --> 00:31:17,380
[SPEAKER_00] Oholost.

822
00:31:17,380 --> 00:31:20,319
[SPEAKER_00] Ona je ta majka svih grijeha.

823
00:31:20,319 --> 00:31:21,900
[SPEAKER_00] Tu se zašto ogovaram?

824
00:31:21,900 --> 00:31:23,440
[SPEAKER_00] Pa jer sam nesiguran u sebe.

825
00:31:23,440 --> 00:31:28,160
[SPEAKER_00] Jer mislim ako prokažem tuđe manetu da se ja možda malko bolji.

826
00:31:28,160 --> 00:31:31,579
[SPEAKER_00] Ogovaram iz slabosti, iz svog jada.

827
00:31:31,579 --> 00:31:34,799
[SPEAKER_00] Neko možda, ne daj Bože, možda čak i zločije.

828
00:31:35,660 --> 00:31:38,799
[SPEAKER_00] Osto kad riče o klevetama, kad se spremno kleveta druge osobe,

829
00:31:38,799 --> 00:31:43,480
[SPEAKER_00] to pokazuje jednu nesretnu osobu, jednu nesretno srce,

830
00:31:43,480 --> 00:31:46,779
[SPEAKER_00] jednu nesređenu nutrinu osobe koja je kadra to učiniti.

831
00:31:46,779 --> 00:31:49,279
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ona to onda mora otkriti.

832
00:31:49,279 --> 00:31:50,980
[SPEAKER_00] Bože moj, kako sam jadan.

833
00:31:50,980 --> 00:31:52,960
[SPEAKER_00] Pomozi mi.

834
00:31:52,960 --> 00:31:58,299
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, puno je važnije, to nutarnije otkriti zašto se događa to,

835
00:31:58,299 --> 00:31:59,839
[SPEAKER_00] zašto ja ponadjam te grijehe.

836
00:31:59,839 --> 00:32:02,339
[SPEAKER_00] Otkretu ono dominantnu vlasti nutrini,

837
00:32:02,339 --> 00:32:05,740
[SPEAKER_00] oko tog dominantnu se okreću u moji svakodnevni životni izbori,

838
00:32:05,740 --> 00:32:09,200
[SPEAKER_00] životne odluge koje vode onda do jednog, drugog, trećeg, malog ili velikog grijeha.

839
00:32:09,200 --> 00:32:16,099
[SPEAKER_00] I onda ispovijed će biti praktički jedan zaokret kao kruna procesa obraćenja,

840
00:32:16,099 --> 00:32:19,279
[SPEAKER_00] doveće doista do promjene u mome životu.

841
00:32:19,279 --> 00:32:26,500
[SPEAKER_00] U ovom procesu u kojem je ispovijed praktički kruna procesa obraćenja,

842
00:32:26,500 --> 00:32:30,779
[SPEAKER_00] jedan je jedini način da to ispravno doživim,

843
00:32:31,059 --> 00:32:33,079
[SPEAKER_00] a to je u podnožu Kristova križa.

844
00:32:33,079 --> 00:32:37,900
[SPEAKER_00] Bez Kristova križa ja ne razumim težinu grijeha.

845
00:32:37,900 --> 00:32:40,140
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ne mogu razumjeti strahotu grijeha.

846
00:32:40,140 --> 00:32:44,700
[SPEAKER_00] Tek u podnožu njegova križa ja otkrivam kako je grijeh njega razapeo.

847
00:32:44,700 --> 00:32:46,680
[SPEAKER_00] Moj grijeh je njega razapeo.

848
00:32:47,539 --> 00:32:48,819
[SPEAKER_00] I moj grijeh je bio tu.

849
00:32:48,819 --> 00:32:55,380
[SPEAKER_00] I to me mora neki način prestraviti, ne iz straha od kazne,

850
00:32:55,380 --> 00:33:01,980
[SPEAKER_00] nego iz straha od nemara, straha od ne ljubavi,

851
00:33:01,980 --> 00:33:05,440
[SPEAKER_00] straha od prijezira prema gospodinu koji me toliko ljubi.

852
00:33:05,880 --> 00:33:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] I to me onda mora motivirati da živim svetim životom.

853
00:33:09,000 --> 00:33:13,200
[SPEAKER_01] Naime, sad kad govorimo o ovim malo težim temama,

854
00:33:13,200 --> 00:33:16,559
[SPEAKER_01] kada gledamo kako bi se korizma trebala živjeti unutar jedne obitelji,

855
00:33:16,559 --> 00:33:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] koje su aktivnosti tu primjerene i za djecu, za roditelje,

856
00:33:20,000 --> 00:33:21,099
[SPEAKER_01] kako da se to živi?

857
00:33:21,099 --> 00:33:26,400
[SPEAKER_00] Da. Pa to je jedna sad jako zanimljiva i bremenita tema.

858
00:33:26,400 --> 00:33:32,900
[SPEAKER_00] Ali svakako ja vjerujem da upravo živjeti korizmu u obitelji

859
00:33:32,900 --> 00:33:38,319
[SPEAKER_00] može silno pomoći obitelji da postane obitelj.

860
00:33:38,319 --> 00:33:40,519
[SPEAKER_00] Da postane kako je crkva, recimo zamišlja.

861
00:33:40,519 --> 00:33:43,220
[SPEAKER_00] Crkva predstavlja dokumentijom drugog vatikanskog obitelj

862
00:33:43,220 --> 00:33:45,099
[SPEAKER_00] kao domaću kućnu crkvu.

863
00:33:45,099 --> 00:33:50,279
[SPEAKER_00] Svaka je obitelj slika prestavog trojstva pozvana biti kućna crkva.

864
00:33:50,279 --> 00:33:51,400
[SPEAKER_00] Sad zamislite ovako.

865
00:33:51,400 --> 00:33:55,740
[SPEAKER_00] Kada bi kroz vrijeme korizme muži, žena i djeca

866
00:33:55,740 --> 00:34:01,140
[SPEAKER_00] od prvog odbuđenja samo sa postini mislima

867
00:34:01,140 --> 00:34:02,400
[SPEAKER_00] pristupali jednim drugima.

868
00:34:02,400 --> 00:34:04,500
[SPEAKER_00] Roditelji spune o ljubavi prema djeci,

869
00:34:04,500 --> 00:34:05,819
[SPEAKER_00] a najprije jednu prema drugome,

870
00:34:05,819 --> 00:34:08,380
[SPEAKER_00] jer ubiti njihova ljubav, izvor te obitelji

871
00:34:08,380 --> 00:34:10,699
[SPEAKER_00] i djeca, osobitno kad su malena,

872
00:34:10,699 --> 00:34:13,599
[SPEAKER_00] oni žive od ljubavi kojom se roditelji ljube.

873
00:34:13,599 --> 00:34:17,079
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, od poštivanja ljubavi koje roditelji pokazuju jedno drugome.

874
00:34:17,079 --> 00:34:18,719
[SPEAKER_00] To je hrana djeci.

875
00:34:19,340 --> 00:34:20,539
[SPEAKER_00] To je hrana djeci.

876
00:34:20,539 --> 00:34:21,739
[SPEAKER_00] E sada,

877
00:34:21,739 --> 00:34:24,320
[SPEAKER_00] naš ritam života

878
00:34:24,320 --> 00:34:27,719
[SPEAKER_00] tako dovede sve nas,

879
00:34:27,719 --> 00:34:29,059
[SPEAKER_00] pa i nas većenike,

880
00:34:29,059 --> 00:34:30,719
[SPEAKER_00] da postanemo čangrizavi,

881
00:34:30,719 --> 00:34:31,920
[SPEAKER_00] da postanemo nervozni,

882
00:34:31,920 --> 00:34:32,340
[SPEAKER_00] da potkažemo,

883
00:34:32,380 --> 00:34:36,460
[SPEAKER_00] pa šta nervozan sam, onda se iskalimo na članima obitelji.

884
00:34:36,460 --> 00:34:39,460
[SPEAKER_00] Znamislimo drugačiju situaciju.

885
00:34:39,460 --> 00:34:43,440
[SPEAKER_00] Ponoviću da jednim drugima pristupamo sa puno nježnosti,

886
00:34:43,440 --> 00:34:44,679
[SPEAKER_00] sa puno ljubavi.

887
00:34:44,679 --> 00:34:47,300
[SPEAKER_00] I kad drugi pogriješi, da ja znamo prostiti,

888
00:34:47,300 --> 00:34:48,679
[SPEAKER_00] da znamo pružiti ruku,

889
00:34:48,679 --> 00:34:49,719
[SPEAKER_00] da znamo hrabriti,

890
00:34:49,719 --> 00:34:53,760
[SPEAKER_00] kako bi život u obitelji postao puno ljepši.

891
00:34:54,440 --> 00:34:56,900
[SPEAKER_00] Kako bi mladi tu se osjetili ohrabrani,

892
00:34:56,900 --> 00:34:57,559
[SPEAKER_00] da ne bježe,

893
00:34:57,559 --> 00:34:58,880
[SPEAKER_00] jer ih roditelji ne razume.

894
00:34:58,880 --> 00:35:01,519
[SPEAKER_00] Ja često puta pričam ovako sa mladim,

895
00:35:01,519 --> 00:35:02,219
[SPEAKER_00] kad zatražem razgovor,

896
00:35:02,219 --> 00:35:02,340
[SPEAKER_00] kaže,

897
00:35:02,340 --> 00:35:03,579
[SPEAKER_00] a oni mene ne razume.

898
00:35:03,579 --> 00:35:05,679
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro, ja često puta uzvratim,

899
00:35:05,679 --> 00:35:07,179
[SPEAKER_00] razumiti li ti njih?

900
00:35:07,179 --> 00:35:09,519
[SPEAKER_00] Treba obostano razumijevanje.

901
00:35:09,840 --> 00:35:12,840
[SPEAKER_00] Ali svakako korizma može biti tu osiljne pomoći,

902
00:35:12,840 --> 00:35:16,679
[SPEAKER_00] osobito ako se vrati obiteljska molitva

903
00:35:16,679 --> 00:35:18,400
[SPEAKER_00] u središte obiteljskog života.

904
00:35:18,400 --> 00:35:21,460
[SPEAKER_00] E to može biti onda izvor velikih blagoslova

905
00:35:21,460 --> 00:35:23,900
[SPEAKER_00] i, rekao bih, ujedinjenja obitelji

906
00:35:23,900 --> 00:35:25,960
[SPEAKER_00] i onda se obitelji, članovi obitelji

907
00:35:25,960 --> 00:35:27,559
[SPEAKER_00] puno dublje povezuju.

908
00:35:27,559 --> 00:35:31,019
[SPEAKER_00] Onda osjećaju biti da oni to znali ili ne znali,

909
00:35:31,019 --> 00:35:32,639
[SPEAKER_00] ali tada intuitivno naslučuju

910
00:35:32,639 --> 00:35:34,340
[SPEAKER_00] da osim njih člana obitelji,

911
00:35:34,340 --> 00:35:35,539
[SPEAKER_00] da je još netko tu.

912
00:35:35,539 --> 00:35:36,900
[SPEAKER_00] Gospodin je tu.

913
00:35:36,900 --> 00:35:39,500
[SPEAKER_00] On je tu u njihovu životu.

914
00:35:39,500 --> 00:35:40,679
[SPEAKER_00] On ih blagosilja.

915
00:35:40,679 --> 00:35:43,320
[SPEAKER_00] On od njih stvara sliku trojstva.

916
00:35:43,320 --> 00:35:46,380
[SPEAKER_00] On stvara kućnu crkvu od njihova obiteljskog zajedništva.

917
00:35:46,380 --> 00:35:48,119
[SPEAKER_01] Sad kad govorimo o obitelji,

918
00:35:48,119 --> 00:35:49,860
[SPEAKER_01] možemo se nadovezati na svetog Josipa,

919
00:35:49,860 --> 00:35:51,780
[SPEAKER_01] kojeg isto tako slavimo kroz ovaj period.

920
00:35:51,780 --> 00:35:54,699
[SPEAKER_01] Kako biste sada možda se nadovezali,

921
00:35:54,699 --> 00:35:56,360
[SPEAKER_01] što bi provučili možda očevima,

922
00:35:56,360 --> 00:35:58,480
[SPEAKER_01] a u ovom smislu, po uzoru na svetoga Josipa?

923
00:35:58,480 --> 00:35:59,739
[SPEAKER_01] Što možemo njega naučiti?

924
00:35:59,739 --> 00:36:02,159
[SPEAKER_00] Josip je silan.

925
00:36:02,159 --> 00:36:05,760
[SPEAKER_00] Josip je silan svetac.

926
00:36:05,760 --> 00:36:09,159
[SPEAKER_00] Crkva kaže u svom nauku

927
00:36:09,159 --> 00:36:12,300
[SPEAKER_00] da kad dragi Bog poziva nekoga na neko poslanje,

928
00:36:12,300 --> 00:36:14,780
[SPEAKER_00] redovito mu daje i dostatne darove

929
00:36:14,780 --> 00:36:16,699
[SPEAKER_00] da može izvršiti to poslanje.

930
00:36:16,699 --> 00:36:18,840
[SPEAKER_00] A koje je bilo poslanje svetog Josipa?

931
00:36:18,840 --> 00:36:20,340
[SPEAKER_00] Da bude branitelj,

932
00:36:20,340 --> 00:36:21,960
[SPEAKER_00] hranitelj,

933
00:36:21,960 --> 00:36:23,860
[SPEAKER_00] poočin Božjem sinu.

934
00:36:24,340 --> 00:36:28,800
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, gospodin Bog, nebeski otac, ima povjerenja u jednog čovjeka,

935
00:36:28,800 --> 00:36:31,820
[SPEAKER_00] kad mu povjerava ono najdragocinije,

936
00:36:31,820 --> 00:36:34,239
[SPEAKER_00] kad mu povjerava svoga sina,

937
00:36:34,239 --> 00:36:35,900
[SPEAKER_00] svog nerođenog sina,

938
00:36:35,900 --> 00:36:39,320
[SPEAKER_00] da Josip skrbi o njemu kao vlastiti otac,

939
00:36:39,320 --> 00:36:41,159
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno kao otac o vlastitom sinu.

940
00:36:41,159 --> 00:36:42,980
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, to je silno.

941
00:36:42,980 --> 00:36:45,639
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ja razmišljam o Josipu, pa kažem,

942
00:36:45,719 --> 00:36:49,780
[SPEAKER_00] Božem moj, kakvim je on morao biti krepostima urešen,

943
00:36:49,780 --> 00:36:50,780
[SPEAKER_00] darovima urešen,

944
00:36:50,780 --> 00:36:53,079
[SPEAKER_00] da je mogao obaviti tu zadaću.

945
00:36:53,079 --> 00:36:55,480
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko je povjerenje, gospodin Bog ima u njega.

946
00:36:55,480 --> 00:36:58,579
[SPEAKER_00] Sve to čim je on bio obdaren, ispunjen,

947
00:36:58,579 --> 00:36:59,739
[SPEAKER_00] sve to pismo,

948
00:36:59,739 --> 00:37:01,840
[SPEAKER_00] Mato je evanđelje, sažimao jednu riječ.

949
00:37:01,840 --> 00:37:04,059
[SPEAKER_00] Bijaše muž pravedan.

950
00:37:04,059 --> 00:37:06,139
[SPEAKER_00] Ako se približimo Josipu,

951
00:37:06,139 --> 00:37:08,099
[SPEAKER_00] vidimo prema evanđeljima,

952
00:37:08,099 --> 00:37:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] on neizgovara ni jednu riječ.

953
00:37:10,000 --> 00:37:12,280
[SPEAKER_00] Njega pismo, Matej,

954
00:37:12,280 --> 00:37:14,039
[SPEAKER_00] manje luka, više Matej,

955
00:37:14,079 --> 00:37:16,679
[SPEAKER_00] predstavlja kao čovjeka koji sluša.

956
00:37:16,679 --> 00:37:19,340
[SPEAKER_00] Ono sluškuje Božije planove.

957
00:37:19,340 --> 00:37:21,619
[SPEAKER_00] On se pita što Bog tu želi.

958
00:37:21,619 --> 00:37:25,019
[SPEAKER_00] I kad otkrije ponekad ponutanjem viđenju,

959
00:37:25,019 --> 00:37:27,639
[SPEAKER_00] ponekad u snovima, kako kaže Matej,

960
00:37:27,639 --> 00:37:29,579
[SPEAKER_00] onda on ima samo jedan put

961
00:37:29,579 --> 00:37:32,159
[SPEAKER_00] izvršiti što Bog od njega očekuje.

962
00:37:32,159 --> 00:37:34,019
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, to je čovjek

963
00:37:34,019 --> 00:37:36,380
[SPEAKER_00] u kojem, rekao bih,

964
00:37:36,380 --> 00:37:39,199
[SPEAKER_00] koji je sebe podlažući sebe Božjim zapovjedima,

965
00:37:39,199 --> 00:37:41,079
[SPEAKER_00] koje je on naučio jako dobro,

966
00:37:41,079 --> 00:37:42,860
[SPEAKER_00] još kao maleni židov,

967
00:37:43,019 --> 00:37:45,900
[SPEAKER_00] koje otkriva u pismu Starog Zavjeta,

968
00:37:45,900 --> 00:37:47,079
[SPEAKER_00] on sebe podlaži,

969
00:37:47,079 --> 00:37:49,320
[SPEAKER_00] i to podlaganje Bogu i njegovim zapovjedima

970
00:37:49,320 --> 00:37:51,699
[SPEAKER_00] dovodi do ravnoteža u njegovu životu.

971
00:37:51,699 --> 00:37:53,239
[SPEAKER_00] On je stabilan čovjek.

972
00:37:53,239 --> 00:37:55,460
[SPEAKER_00] On je čovjek vršenja.

973
00:37:55,460 --> 00:37:58,199
[SPEAKER_00] Čovjek, evo, kad on otkrije što Bog želi,

974
00:37:58,199 --> 00:37:59,199
[SPEAKER_00] on nema, ponovit ću,

975
00:37:59,199 --> 00:38:00,519
[SPEAKER_00] samo ima jedan izbor,

976
00:38:00,519 --> 00:38:02,800
[SPEAKER_00] a to je vršiti što Bog od njega očekuje.

977
00:38:03,800 --> 00:38:07,480
[SPEAKER_00] To je čovjek koji se stavlja u službu

978
00:38:07,480 --> 00:38:09,340
[SPEAKER_00] majici i njezinu sinu.

979
00:38:09,340 --> 00:38:10,679
[SPEAKER_00] Majici i djetetu.

980
00:38:10,679 --> 00:38:14,179
[SPEAKER_00] Prije nego što je Ivan Krstelj rekao,

981
00:38:14,179 --> 00:38:16,340
[SPEAKER_00] Krist treba da raste, ja da se omanjujem,

982
00:38:16,340 --> 00:38:17,559
[SPEAKER_00] to je Josip već ostvario.

983
00:38:17,559 --> 00:38:20,619
[SPEAKER_00] U središtu života je Božansko dijete,

984
00:38:20,619 --> 00:38:22,099
[SPEAKER_00] on je potpuno na službi Isusu.

985
00:38:22,099 --> 00:38:26,860
[SPEAKER_00] I to je poziv u biti svakoj kršanskoj obitelji.

986
00:38:26,860 --> 00:38:29,440
[SPEAKER_00] Ako želi bi kršanska uz ono vidljivo,

987
00:38:29,440 --> 00:38:30,420
[SPEAKER_00] uz roditelje, djecu,

988
00:38:30,420 --> 00:38:32,539
[SPEAKER_00] to mora biti, u središku te obitelji

989
00:38:32,539 --> 00:38:33,780
[SPEAKER_00] mora biti onaj nevidljivi,

990
00:38:33,780 --> 00:38:35,079
[SPEAKER_00] a to je gospodin Isus.

991
00:38:35,079 --> 00:38:37,340
[SPEAKER_00] I tek tada ta zajednica ljudi

992
00:38:37,340 --> 00:38:38,679
[SPEAKER_00] povezanih ljudskim vezama,

993
00:38:38,679 --> 00:38:41,239
[SPEAKER_00] ljubavi, predanja, poštovanja,

994
00:38:41,239 --> 00:38:43,719
[SPEAKER_00] ona postaje kućna crkva

995
00:38:43,719 --> 00:38:45,059
[SPEAKER_00] u kojoj na neki način

996
00:38:45,059 --> 00:38:46,500
[SPEAKER_00] gospodin Bog prebiva.

997
00:38:46,500 --> 00:38:48,340
[SPEAKER_00] Ona postaje Božje svetohranište.

998
00:38:48,340 --> 00:38:51,599
[SPEAKER_00] I Josip tu sigurno može biti silno

999
00:38:51,599 --> 00:38:53,780
[SPEAKER_00] nadahnuće kršanskim očevima,

1000
00:38:53,780 --> 00:38:56,099
[SPEAKER_00] kako ne sebično služiti

1001
00:38:56,099 --> 00:38:58,239
[SPEAKER_00] vlastvoj obitelji,

1002
00:38:58,239 --> 00:39:00,039
[SPEAKER_00] vlastvoj suprozi, vlastvoj djeci.

1003
00:39:00,039 --> 00:39:02,400
[SPEAKER_00] I po primjer Josipa,

1004
00:39:02,400 --> 00:39:05,480
[SPEAKER_00] kako to služenje postaje njihov put posvećenja.

1005
00:39:05,480 --> 00:39:09,119
[SPEAKER_00] Postaje način kako oni postaju

1006
00:39:09,119 --> 00:39:10,360
[SPEAKER_00] drugi Josipi.

1007
00:39:10,360 --> 00:39:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] Oni se posvećaju preko služenja

1008
00:39:13,000 --> 00:39:13,980
[SPEAKER_00] vlastvoj obitelji.

1009
00:39:13,980 --> 00:39:15,920
[SPEAKER_01] Domane, hvala vam.

1010
00:39:15,920 --> 00:39:17,400
[SPEAKER_01] Nadam se da će ove smjernici

1011
00:39:17,400 --> 00:39:20,059
[SPEAKER_01] tako biti korisne u ovom periodu korizme.

1012
00:39:20,739 --> 00:39:22,519
[SPEAKER_01] Vama, dragi gledatelji, hvala puno.

1013
00:39:22,519 --> 00:39:25,059
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, vidimo se u trećoj epizodi.

1014
00:39:25,059 --> 00:39:26,820
[SPEAKER_01] Završili smo period korizme.

1015
00:39:26,820 --> 00:39:28,940
[SPEAKER_01] I pratite nas i dalje.

1016
00:39:28,940 --> 00:39:30,079
[SPEAKER_01] Boži blagoslov.

